{"data":[{"date":"07:12 24/07","title":"Barca l\u00ean \u0111\u01b0\u1eddng sang M\u1ef9, Messi v\u1eafng m\u1eb7t","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/6/25/barca-len-duong-sang-my-messi-vang-mat.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Trong danh s\u00e1ch tri\u1ec7u t\u1eadp \u0111\u1ec3 chu\u1ea9n b\u1ecb cho tour du \u0111\u1ea5u h\u00e8 n\u00e0y, Messi kh\u00f4ng c\u00f3 m\u1eb7t trong \u0111\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh c\u1ee7a Barca.\r\n</h2><h2><br>\r\nMessi v\u1eabn ch\u01b0a tr\u1edf l\u1ea1i<br>\r\n&nbsp;</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Tr\u1ea3i qua k\u1ef3 World Cup th\u1ea5t v\u1ecdng khi d\u1eebng b\u01b0\u1edbc ngay \u1edf v\u00f2ng 1/8, El Pulga v\u1eabn \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c cho ngh\u1ec9 tr\u01b0\u1edbc khi b\u01b0\u1edbc v\u00e0o m\u00f9a b\u00f3ng m\u1edbi. Theo th\u00f4ng tin m\u1edbi nh\u1ea5t, Barcelona \u0111\u00e3 l\u00ean danh s\u00e1ch sang M\u1ef9 du \u0111\u1ea5u v\u00e0 h\u1ecd quy\u1ebft \u0111\u1ecbnh \u0111\u1ec3 ng\u00f4i sao s\u00e1ng nh\u1ea5t c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c ngh\u1ec9 ng\u01a1i.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Kh\u00f4ng nh\u1eefng v\u1eady, t\u1ea5t c\u1ea3 c\u00e1c c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 tham d\u1ef1 World Cup 2018 s\u1ebd \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111\u1eb7c c\u00e1ch mi\u1ec5n tham d\u1ef1 tour n\u00e0y, trong \u0111\u00f3 bao g\u1ed3m Luis Suarez, Philippe Coutinho v\u00e0 c\u00e1c c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 c\u1ee7a \u0110T T\u00e2y Ban Nha nh\u01b0 Gerard Pique, Sergio Busquets v\u00e0 Jordi Alba. Nh\u1eefng c\u00e1i t\u00ean g\u00f3p m\u1eb7t \u1edf tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u cu\u1ed1i c\u00f9ng l\u00e0 Samuel Umtiti, Ousmane Dembele (Ph\u00e1p), Ivan Rakitic (Croatia) th\u1eadm ch\u00ed c\u00f2n \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c ngh\u1ec9 x\u1ea3 h\u01a1i \u0111\u1ebfn cu\u1ed1i th\u00e1ng 8.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Messi kh\u00f4ng c\u00f3 m\u1eb7t trong \u0111\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh c\u1ee7a Barca tham d\u1ef1 du \u0111\u1ea5u h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Messi kh\u00f4ng c\u00f3 m\u1eb7t trong \u0111\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh c\u1ee7a Barca tham d\u1ef1 du \u0111\u1ea5u h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/1/Messi-khong-co-mat-trong-doi-hinh-cua-Barca-tham-du-du-dau-hinh-anh.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Messi kh\u00f4ng c\u00f3 m\u1eb7t trong \u0111\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh c\u1ee7a Barca sau k\u1ef3 World Cup 2018</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<div><br>\r\nV\u00e0o h\u00f4m nay, Barca \u0111\u00e3 bay \u0111\u1ebfn Portland, Oregon \u0111\u1ec3 t\u1eadp luy\u1ec7n t\u1ea1i b\u1ea3n doanh c\u1ee7a Nike. Th\u1ea7y tr\u00f2 Ernesto Valverde s\u1ebd ch\u1ea1m tr\u00e1n v\u1edbi Tottenham t\u1ea1i Los Angeles v\u00e0o th\u1ee9 B\u1ea3y, sau \u0111\u00f3 l\u00e0 g\u1eb7p AS Roma t\u1ea1i Dallas v\u00e0 AC Milan \u1edf Santa Clara. \u0110\u00f3 l\u00e0 h\u00e0nh tr\u00ecnh c\u1ee7a \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng x\u1ee9 Catalonia, tr\u01b0\u1edbc khi quay v\u1ec1 chu\u1ea9n b\u1ecb cho La Liga.</div>\r\n<div>&nbsp;</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Tour du \u0111\u1ea5u n\u00e0y d\u00f9 kh\u00f4ng c\u00f3 nh\u1eefng ng\u00f4i sao s\u00e1ng nh\u1ea5t, nh\u01b0ng s\u1ebd l\u00e0 c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i \u0111\u1ec3 Valverde xem gi\u00f2 nh\u1eefng t\u00e2n binh h\u1ecd m\u1edbi \u0111em v\u1ec1 nh\u01b0 Arthur Melo v\u00e0 Clement Lenglet. Ng\u01b0\u1ee3c l\u1ea1i, nh\u1eefng c\u00e1i t\u00ean n\u1eb1m trong danh s\u00e1ch nguy hi\u1ec3m g\u1ed3m Andre Gomes, Lucas Digne v\u00e0 Rafinha c\u0169ng c\u00f3 m\u1eb7t trong chuy\u1ebfn \u0111i n\u00e0y.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">C\u00f9ng v\u1edbi \u0111\u00f3 l\u00e0 13 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 \u1edf \u0111\u1ed9i B c\u0169ng tham gia c\u00f9ng to\u00e0n \u0111\u1ed9i. M\u1ecdi th\u1ee9 t\u1ea5t nhi\u00ean kh\u00f4ng ph\u1ea3i v\u1ea5n \u0111\u1ec1 v\u1edbi HLV Valverde, nh\u01b0ng \u0111\u1ed1i v\u1edbi c\u00e1c C\u0110V t\u1ea1i M\u1ef9, s\u1ebd l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t n\u1ed7i th\u1ea5t v\u1ecdng l\u1edbn khi Messi kh\u00f4ng c\u00f3 m\u1eb7t trong \u0111\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh c\u1ee7a Barca.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"\" title=\"\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/24/bar.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Danh s\u00e1ch h\u1ed9i qu\u00e2n c\u1ee7a Barca tham d\u1ef1 tour du \u0111\u1ea5u</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<h3>&nbsp;</h3>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/bong-da-tbn/tan-binh-cua-barca-tho-phao-vi-khong-con-phai-so-messi-180-191789.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/22/tan-binh-cua-barca-tho-phao-vi-khong-con-phai-so-messi.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/bong-da-tbn/tan-binh-cua-barca-tho-phao-vi-khong-con-phai-so-messi-180-191789.html\">T\u00e2n binh c\u1ee7a Barca th\u1edf ph\u00e0o v\u00ec kh\u00f4ng c\u00f2n ph\u1ea3i s\u1ee3 Messi</span><br>\r\nTrung v\u1ec7 m\u1edbi gia nh\u1eadp Barca t\u1eeb Sevilla, Clement Lenglet chia s\u1ebb v\u1ec1 Messi v\u1edbi s\u1ef1 t\u00f4n tr\u1ecdng r\u1ea5t l\u1edbn.</div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/tin-chuyen-nhuong/gui-de-nghi-lan-3-barca-quyet-mua-ngoi-sao-cua-chelsea-187-191704.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/10/gui-de-nghi-lan-3-barca-quyet-mua-ngoi-sao-cua-chelsea.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/tin-chuyen-nhuong/gui-de-nghi-lan-3-barca-quyet-mua-ngoi-sao-cua-chelsea-187-191704.html\">G\u1eedi \u0111\u1ec1 ngh\u1ecb l\u1ea7n 3, Barca quy\u1ebft mua ng\u00f4i sao c\u1ee7a Chelsea</span><br>\r\nTheo b\u00e1o gi\u1edbi Anh, CLB Barcelona v\u1eeba \u0111\u01b0a ra \u0111\u1ec1 ngh\u1ecb l\u1ea7n th\u1ee9 ba \u0111\u1ec3 h\u1ecfi mua ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 ch\u1ea1y c\u00e1nh Willian t\u1eeb Chelsea.</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Nguy\u1ec7t Anh (TTVN)</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"1565","checkdouble":"191877"},{"date":"07:27 24/07","title":"Xu\u1ea5t hi\u1ec7n di\u1ec5n bi\u1ebfn kh\u00f4ng t\u01b0\u1edfng m\u00e0n \u201cc\u01b0\u1edbp d\u00e2u\u201d th\u01b0\u01a1ng v\u1ee5 Malcolm","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/20/xuat-hien-dien-bien-khong-tuong-man-cuop-dau-thuong-vu-malcolm.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Sau m\u1ed9t k\u1ef3 World Cup th\u1ea3m h\u1ea1i v\u1edbi scandal l\u1edbn, B\u00f2 t\u00f3t \u0111\u00e3 quy\u1ebft \u0111\u1ecbnh thay t\u01b0\u1edbng. M\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y, ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o David Villa \u1ee7ng h\u1ed9 HLV Luis Enrique \u0111em l\u1ea1i th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng cho \u0110T.</h2><h2><br>\r\nVilla mu\u1ed1n T\u00e2y Ban Nha l\u00ean ng\u00f4i v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch<br>\r\n&nbsp;</h2>\r\n<div>Tr\u01b0\u1edbc khi World Cup 2018 di\u1ec5n ra 1 ng\u00e0y, \u0110T T\u00e2y Ban Nha ch\u00ednh th\u1ee9c sa th\u1ea3i HLV Julen Lopetegui v\u00e0 b\u1ed5 nhi\u1ec7m Fernando Hierro thay th\u1ebf. Sau gi\u1ea3i, Hierro c\u0169ng r\u1eddi kh\u1ecfi chi\u1ebfc gh\u1ebf n\u00f3ng v\u00e0 nh\u01b0\u1eddng ch\u1ed7 cho Luis Enrique &ndash; c\u1ef1u HLV c\u1ee7a Barca, v\u00e0 t\u1eebng kho\u00e1c \u00e1o c\u1ea3 2 \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng h\u00e0ng \u0111\u1ea7u La Liga khi c\u00f2n thi \u0111\u1ea5u.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">B\u1ecf qua s\u1ef1 th\u1ea5t v\u1ecdng tr\u00ean \u0111\u1ea5t Nga, B\u00f2 t\u00f3t c\u1ea7n ph\u1ea3i th\u1ec3 hi\u1ec7n \u0111\u1eb3ng c\u1ea5p v\u1ed1n c\u00f3 v\u00e0 h\u01b0\u1edbng t\u1edbi ch\u1ee9c v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch EURO 2020. M\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y, ch\u00e2n s\u00fat k\u1ef3 c\u1ef1u David Villa \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 nh\u1eefng l\u1eddi chia s\u1ebb v\u1ec1 Enrique: &ldquo;Th\u00e1ch th\u1ee9c \u0111\u1eb7t ra cho \u00f4ng r\u1ea5t l\u00e0 r\u1ea5t l\u1edbn, b\u1edfi \u0110T \u0111\u00e3 gi\u00e0nh \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c m\u1ecdi danh hi\u1ec7u trong nh\u1eefng gi\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ea5u \u0111\u1ec9nh cao.&rdquo;<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<div style=\"width: 100%;\" class=\"imagecontainer\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"width: 100%;\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"David Villa \u1ee7ng h\u1ed9 HLV Luis Enrique\" title=\"HLV Luis Enrique\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2017/1/23/dai-thang-eibar-hlv-enrique-van-chua-hai-long.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>David Villa \u1ee7ng h\u1ed9 HLV Luis Enrique</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div><br>\r\n&ldquo;T\u00f4i kh\u00f4ng c\u00f3 m\u1eb7t t\u1ea1i World Cup 2018, v\u00ec v\u1eady th\u1eadt kh\u00f3 \u0111\u1ec3 n\u00f3i v\u1ec1 nh\u1eefng g\u00ec \u0111\u00e3 di\u1ec5n ra. Th\u1eadt kh\u00f3 \u0111\u1ec3 nh\u00ecn nh\u1eadn v\u1ea5n \u0111\u1ec1 khi b\u1ea1n kh\u00f4ng t\u1eadn m\u1eaft ch\u1ee9ng ki\u1ebfn. T\u00f4i ngh\u0129 v\u1ec1 b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 nhi\u1ec1u h\u01a1n nh\u1eefng g\u00ec b\u00ean ngo\u00e0i s\u00e2n c\u1ecf. N\u1ebfu b\u1ea1n l\u00e0m \u0111\u00fang, c\u00f3 m\u1ed9t chi\u1ebfn thu\u1eadt t\u1ed1t, b\u1ea1n th\u1eafng. N\u1ebfu kh\u00f4ng, b\u1ea1n th\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i, \u0111\u01a1n gi\u1ea3n l\u00e0 v\u1eady.&rdquo;</div>\r\n<div>&nbsp;</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&ldquo;Khi \u0111\u1ed1i m\u1eb7t v\u1edbi nh\u1eefng \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng c\u00f3 ngu\u1ed3n \u0111\u1ed9ng l\u1ef1c l\u1edbn, b\u1ea1n c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 th\u1ea5y \u0110T Nga c\u00f3 m\u1ed9t k\u1ef3 World Cup tuy\u1ec7t v\u1eddi, nh\u1eefng g\u00ec h\u1ecd th\u1ec3 hi\u1ec7n tr\u01b0\u1edbc Croatia \u1edf v\u00f2ng t\u1ee9 k\u1ebft. \u0110\u00f3 l\u00e0 l\u00fd do h\u1ecd ti\u1ec5n T\u00e2y Ban Nha v\u1ec1 n\u01b0\u1edbc v\u1edbi chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng \u1edf v\u00f2ng 1/8. \u0110\u00f3 l\u00e0 nh\u1eefng g\u00ec b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 di\u1ec5n ra, b\u1ea1n ph\u1ea3i l\u00e0m t\u1ea5t c\u1ea3 nh\u1eefng g\u00ec c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 \u0111\u1ec3 gi\u00e0nh th\u1eafng l\u1ee3i.&rdquo;<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&ldquo;Gi\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ea5u ti\u1ebfp theo s\u1ebd l\u00e0 EURO 2020, v\u00ec v\u1eady \u00f4ng \u1ea5y s\u1ebd ph\u1ea3i l\u1eafp r\u00e1p \u0111\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh \u0111\u1ea1t ch\u1ea5t l\u01b0\u1ee3ng cao nh\u1ea5t, sau \u0111\u00f3 b\u01b0\u1edbc v\u00e0o gi\u1ea3i v\u1edbi nh\u1eefng ng\u00f4i sao xu\u1ea5t s\u1eafc nh\u1ea5t c\u00f3 th\u1ec3. D\u00f9 sao v\u1edbi t\u00e0i n\u0103ng hu\u1ea5n luy\u1ec7n, t\u00f4i hy v\u1ecdng \u00f4ng \u1ea5y s\u1ebd \u0111em l\u1ea1i nh\u1eefng \u0111i\u1ec1u t\u1ed1t nh\u1ea5t cho \u0110T T\u00e2y Ban Nha&rdquo; &ndash; David Villa \u1ee7ng h\u1ed9 HLV Luis Enrique.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;<br>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/bong-da-chau-au/luis-enrique-tu-tin-tai-thiet-tay-ban-nha-184-191508.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/10/luis-enrique-tu-tin-tai-thiet-tay-ban-nha.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/bong-da-chau-au/luis-enrique-tu-tin-tai-thiet-tay-ban-nha-184-191508.html\">Luis Enrique t\u1ef1 tin t\u00e1i thi\u1ebft T\u00e2y Ban Nha</span><br>\r\nT\u00e2n HLV 48 tu\u1ed5i tuy\u00ean b\u1ed1 s\u1eb5n s\u00e0ng cho nh\u1eefng th\u1eed th\u00e1ch tr\u00ean gh\u1ebf n\u00f3ng \u0111\u1ed9i tuy\u1ec3n qu\u1ed1c gia n\u01b0\u1edbc nh\u00e0.</div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/ldbd-tay-ban-nha-nai-ni-pique-dung-chia-tay-dtqg-421-190823.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/6/26/ldbd-tay-ban-nha-nai-ni-pique-dung-chia-tay-dtqg.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/ldbd-tay-ban-nha-nai-ni-pique-dung-chia-tay-dtqg-421-190823.html\">L\u0110B\u0110 T\u00e2y Ban Nha n\u00e0i n\u1ec9 Pique \u0111\u1eebng chia tay \u0110TQG</span><br>\r\nGerard Pique chia tay \u0110T T\u00e2y Ban Nha sau World Cup 2018 l\u00e0 d\u1ef1 \u0111\u1ecbnh c\u1ee7a c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 n\u00e0y, song L\u0110B\u0110 x\u1ee9 s\u1edf B\u00f2 t\u00f3t mu\u1ed1n ng\u00f4i sao c\u1ee7a Barca thay \u0111\u1ed5i quy\u1ebft \u0111\u1ecbnh c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh.</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Nguy\u1ec7t Anh (TTVN)</div>\r\n<br></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"1564","checkdouble":"191878"},{"date":"07:50 24/07","title":"Ozil ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c b\u1ecb \u0111\u00e1nh h\u1ed9i \u0111\u1ed3ng t\u1eeb tuy\u1ec3n \u0110\u1ee9c","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/6/27/ozil-tiep-tuc-bi-danh-hoi-dong-tu-tuyen-duc.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>M\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y, huy\u1ec1n tho\u1ea1i Lothar Matthaus ch\u1ec9 tr\u00edch Mesut Ozil sau quy\u1ebft \u0111\u1ecbnh t\u1eeb gi\u00e3 \u0110T qu\u1ed1c gia, v\u00e0 cho r\u1eb1ng c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i \u0111\u1ec3 anh quay l\u1ea1i m\u00e0u \u00e1o n\u00e0y l\u00e0 b\u1eb1ng kh\u00f4ng.\r\n</h2><h2><br>\r\nOzil b\u1ecb huy\u1ec1n tho\u1ea1i ch\u1ec9 tr\u00edch n\u1eb7ng n\u1ec1<br>\r\n&nbsp;</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Sau nh\u1eefng l\u1eddi ch\u00ea tr\u00e1ch t\u1eeb Ch\u1ee7 t\u1ecbch c\u1ee7a Bayern (Uli Hoeness) r\u1eb1ng&hellip; &ldquo;<span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/bong-da-chau-au/ozil-chia-tay-tuyen-duc-chu-tich-bayern-ha-he-mat-sat-184-191852.html\" target=\"_blank\">Ozil \u0111\u00e1 nh\u01b0 c*t trong v\u00e0i n\u0103m qua</span>&rdquo;, c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 n\u00e0y ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c b\u1ecb Li\u00ean \u0111o\u00e0n n\u00e9m \u0111\u00e1. V\u1eabn ch\u01b0a h\u1ebft, m\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y huy\u1ec1n tho\u1ea1i Lothar Matthaus l\u00e0 ng\u01b0\u1eddi nh\u1ea3y v\u00e0o v\u00e0 d\u00e0nh cho c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 Arsenal nh\u1eefng l\u1eddi l\u1ebd n\u1eb7ng n\u1ec1.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&ldquo;T\u00f4i ngh\u0129 b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 l\u00e0 b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1, ch\u00ednh tr\u1ecb l\u00e0 ch\u00ednh tr\u1ecb&rdquo; &ndash; Matthaus cho bi\u1ebft. &ldquo;Mesut \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 nh\u1eefng c\u1ed1ng hi\u1ebfn tuy\u1ec7t v\u1eddi cho n\u01b0\u1edbc \u0110\u1ee9c trong qu\u00e1 kh\u1ee9, nh\u01b0ng kho\u1ea3ng 1 n\u0103m r\u01b0\u1ee1i qua c\u1eadu \u1ea5y \u0111\u00e3 thi \u0111\u1ea5u r\u1ea5t t\u1ec7. Phong \u0111\u1ed9 c\u1ee7a c\u1eadu \u1ea5y kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 so s\u00e1nh v\u1edbi chi\u1ebfn d\u1ecbch l\u00ean ng\u00f4i World Cup 2014.&rdquo;<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&ldquo;T\u00f4i ngh\u0129 th\u1eddi gian \u0111\u1ec3 thi \u0111\u1ea5u cho \u0110T \u0110\u1ee9c c\u1ee7a c\u1eadu \u1ea5y \u0111\u00e3 ch\u1ea5m d\u1ee9t. Kh\u00f4ng ph\u1ea3i nh\u1eefng h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh hay th\u00f4ng \u0111i\u1ec7p ch\u00ednh tr\u1ecb, \u0111i\u1ec1u \u0111\u00f3 kh\u00f4ng quan tr\u1ecdng v\u00e0 t\u00f4i kh\u00f4ng quan t\u00e2m. T\u00f4i ch\u1ec9 nh\u00ecn nh\u1eadn Mesut Ozil d\u01b0\u1edbi t\u01b0 c\u00e1ch c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1, v\u00e0 r\u00f5 r\u00e0ng c\u1eadu \u1ea5y \u0111\u00e3 sa s\u00fat phong \u0111\u1ed9 th\u00ea th\u1ea3m.&rdquo;<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Lothar Matthaus ch\u1ec9 tr\u00edch Mesut Ozil th\u1eadm t\u1ec7 h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Lothar Matthaus ch\u1ec9 tr\u00edch Mesut Ozil th\u1eadm t\u1ec7 h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/23/Lothar-Matthaus-chi-trich-Mesut-Ozil-tham-te-hinh-anh.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Lothar Matthaus ch\u1ec9 tr\u00edch Mesut Ozil th\u1eadm t\u1ec7</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<div><br>\r\n&ldquo;Ch\u00fang t\u00f4i c\u00f2n r\u1ea5t nhi\u1ec1u c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ch\u1ea5t l\u01b0\u1ee3ng s\u1eb5n s\u00e0ng thay th\u1ebf nh\u1eefng c\u00e1i t\u00ean kh\u00f4ng c\u00f2n gi\u1eef \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c phong \u0111\u1ed9. \u0110T \u0110\u1ee9c \u0111\u00e3 b\u1ecb h\u1ea1 g\u1ee5c b\u1edfi Mexico v\u00e0 H\u00e0n Qu\u1ed1c, \u0111\u00f3 kh\u00f4ng h\u1eb3n l\u00e0 l\u1ed7i c\u1ee7a Ozil. Nh\u01b0ng c\u1eadu \u1ea5y l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t ph\u1ea7n c\u1ee7a \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng v\u00e0 kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 hi\u1ec7n \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c b\u1ea3n th\u00e2n l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t nh\u00e0 l\u00e3nh \u0111\u1ea1o, \u0111i\u1ec1u \u0111\u00e3 di\u1ec5n ra trong 2 n\u0103m qua.&rdquo;</div>\r\n<div>&nbsp;</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&ldquo;V\u1edbi t\u00f4i, v\u1ea5n \u0111\u1ec1 l\u00e0 Ozil kh\u00f4ng c\u00f2n c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 gi\u00fap cho \u0110T \u0110\u1ee9c n\u1eefa. Gi\u1edd l\u00e0 l\u00fac \u0111\u1ec3 \u0111\u01b0a ra s\u1ef1 thay \u0111\u1ed5i. V\u1ec1 v\u1ea5n \u0111\u1ec1 ph\u00e2n bi\u1ec7t ch\u1ee7ng t\u1ed9c, tuy\u1ec7t \u0111\u1ed1i kh\u00f4ng c\u00f3 \u0111i\u1ec1u n\u00e0y. Ch\u00fang t\u00f4i lu\u00f4n m\u1edf c\u1eeda ch\u00e0o \u0111\u00f3n t\u1ea5t c\u1ea3 t\u1edbi n\u01b0\u1edbc \u0110\u1ee9c. Mesut Ozil \u0111\u00e3 thi \u0111\u1ea5u cho \u0110T 10 n\u0103m qua, Sami Khedira, Jerome Boateng hay Serge Gnabry c\u0169ng v\u1eady.&rdquo;<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&ldquo;T\u00f4i ngh\u0129 ch\u00fang t\u00f4i ch\u1eb3ng c\u00f3 v\u1ea5n \u0111\u1ec1 g\u00ec c\u1ea3. <strong>Ng\u01b0\u1eddi th\u1ef1c s\u1ef1 c\u00f3 v\u1ea5n \u0111\u1ec1 \u1edf \u0111\u00e2y ch\u00ednh l\u00e0 c\u1eadu \u1ea5y&rdquo;</strong> &ndash; Lothar Matthaus ch\u1ec9 tr\u00edch Mesut Ozil.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/bong-da-chau-au/ldbd-duc-phan-phao-ozil-sau-cao-buoc-phan-biet-chung-toc-184-191871.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/23/ldbd-duc-phan-phao-ozil-sau-cao-buoc-phan-biet-chung-toc.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/bong-da-chau-au/ldbd-duc-phan-phao-ozil-sau-cao-buoc-phan-biet-chung-toc-184-191871.html\">L\u0110B\u0110 \u0110\u1ee9c ph\u1ea3n ph\u00e1o Ozil sau c\u00e1o bu\u1ed9c ph\u00e2n bi\u1ec7t ch\u1ee7ng t\u1ed9c</span><br>\r\nL\u0110B\u0110 \u0110\u1ee9c ch\u00ednh th\u1ee9c \u0111\u01b0a ra th\u00f4ng b\u00e1o ph\u1ea3n ph\u00e1o nh\u1eefng l\u1eddi ch\u1ec9 tr\u00edch, c\u00e1o bu\u1ed9c ph\u00e2n bi\u1ec7t ch\u1ee7ng t\u1ed9c \u0111\u1ebfn t\u1eeb Mesut Ozil, sau khi ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 29 tu\u1ed5i quy\u1ebft \u0111\u1ecbnh gi\u00e3 t\u1eeb...</div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/bong-da-chau-au/ozil-chia-tay-tuyen-duc-chu-tich-bayern-ha-he-mat-sat-184-191852.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/6/28/ozil-chia-tay-tuyen-duc-chu-tich-bayern-ha-he-mat-sat.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/bong-da-chau-au/ozil-chia-tay-tuyen-duc-chu-tich-bayern-ha-he-mat-sat-184-191852.html\">Ozil chia tay tuy\u1ec3n \u0110\u1ee9c, ch\u1ee7 t\u1ecbch Bayern h\u1ea3 h\u00ea m\u1ea1t s\u00e1t</span><br>\r\nUli Hoeness vui m\u1eebng v\u1edbi quy\u1ebft \u0111\u1ecbnh t\u1eeb gi\u00e3 s\u1ef1 nghi\u1ec7p qu\u1ed1c t\u1ebf c\u1ee7a Mesut Ozil v\u00e0 th\u1eadm ch\u00ed x\u00fac ph\u1ea1m th\u1eb3ng m\u1eb7t ng\u00f4i sao Arsenal.</div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/nhan-vat/tam-thu-cua-mesut-ozil-giot-nuoc-tran-ly-389-191838.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/23/tam-thu-cua-mesut-ozil-giot-nuoc-tran-ly.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/nhan-vat/tam-thu-cua-mesut-ozil-giot-nuoc-tran-ly-389-191838.html\">T\u00e2m th\u01b0 c\u1ee7a Mesut Ozil: Gi\u1ecdt n\u01b0\u1edbc tr\u00e0n ly</span><br>\r\nSau th\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i \u1edf World Cup 2018 c\u1ee7a tuy\u1ec3n \u0110\u1ee9c, Mesut Ozil l\u00e0 t\u00e2m \u0111i\u1ec3m c\u1ee7a ch\u1ec9 tr\u00edch sau b\u1ee9c \u1ea3nh anh v\u00e0 Gundogan ch\u1ee5p c\u00f9ng T\u1ed5ng th\u1ed1ng Th\u1ed5 Nh\u0129 K\u1ef3. Ozil \u0111\u00e3 b\u00e0y t\u1ecf...</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Nguy\u1ec7t Anh (TTVN)</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"1563","checkdouble":"191879"},{"date":"08:01 24/07","title":"Klopp: \u201cN\u0103m nay s\u1ebd l\u00e0 n\u0103m c\u1ee7a ch\u00fang t\u00f4i\u201d","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/24/klopp-nam-nay-se-la-nam-cua-chung-toi.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Sau r\u1ea5t nhi\u1ec1u nh\u1eefng t\u00e2n binh bom t\u1ea5n \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111em v\u1ec1, HLV Jurgen Klopp t\u1ef1 tin gi\u00e0nh danh hi\u1ec7u c\u00f9ng Liverpool.\r\n</h2><h2><br>\r\nThe Kop \u0111\u1eb7t m\u1ee5c ti\u00eau l\u1edbn \u1edf m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i n\u00e0y<br>\r\n&nbsp;</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">4 t\u00e2n binh Naby Keita, Fabinho, Xherdan Shaqiri v\u00e0 Alisson \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111em v\u1ec1 Anfield v\u1edbi m\u1ee9c gi\u00e1 170 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng t\u1ed5ng c\u1ed9ng, gi\u00fap \u0111\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh c\u1ee7a L\u1eef \u0111o\u00e0n \u0111\u1ecf m\u1ea1nh h\u01a1n r\u1ea5t nhi\u1ec1u. \u0110\u00f3 l\u00e0 c\u01a1 s\u1edf v\u00e0 \u0111\u1ed9ng l\u1ef1c \u0111\u1ec3 h\u1ecd gi\u00e0nh ch\u1ee9c v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch Premier League sau bao n\u0103m ch\u1edd \u0111\u1ee3i.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Chia s\u1ebb v\u1ec1 \u0111i\u1ec1u n\u00e0y, HLV Jurgen Klopp th\u1eeba nh\u1eadn: &ldquo;T\u00f4i c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 hi\u1ec3u v\u1ec1 k\u1ef3 v\u1ecdng c\u1ee7a ng\u01b0\u1eddi h\u00e2m m\u1ed9. T\u00f4i kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 \u0111\u1ea3m b\u1ea3o v\u1ec1 ch\u1ee9c v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch, nh\u01b0ng ho\u00e0n to\u00e0n d\u1ec5 hi\u1ec3u khi m\u1ecdi ng\u01b0\u1eddi ngh\u0129 nh\u01b0 v\u1eady. Nh\u1eefng k\u1ef3 v\u1ecdng l\u00e0 \u0111i\u1ec1u r\u1ea5t b\u00ecnh th\u01b0\u1eddng.&rdquo;<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&ldquo;Tr\u01b0\u1edbc h\u1ebft, ch\u00fang t\u00f4i c\u1ea7n ph\u1ea3i tr\u00ecnh di\u1ec5n th\u1ee9 b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 \u0111\u1ee7 s\u1ee9c \u0111em v\u1ec1 nh\u1eefng chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng. Ch\u00fang t\u00f4i kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 n\u00f3i v\u1ec1 ng\u00f4i v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch tr\u01b0\u1edbc khi b\u1eaft \u0111\u1ea7u m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i. T\u00f4i tin r\u1eb1ng \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e3 x\u00e2y d\u1ef1ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c n\u1ec1n t\u1ea3ng v\u1eefng ch\u1eafc \u1edf m\u00f9a tr\u01b0\u1edbc. Tuy nhi\u00ean, b\u1ea1n c\u1ea7n ph\u1ea3i l\u00e0m h\u1ebft s\u1ee9c \u0111\u1ec3 t\u00e1i hi\u1ec7n phong \u0111\u1ed9 nh\u01b0 v\u1eady.&rdquo;<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Klopp t\u1ef1 tin gi\u00e0nh danh hi\u1ec7u c\u00f9ng Liverpool m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i t\u1edbi h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Klopp t\u1ef1 tin gi\u00e0nh danh hi\u1ec7u c\u00f9ng Liverpool m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i t\u1edbi h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/24/klopp.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Jurgen Klopp t\u1ef1 tin gi\u00e0nh danh hi\u1ec7u c\u00f9ng Liverpool</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<div><br>\r\n&ldquo;Ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c th\u1ec3 hi\u1ec7n th\u1ee9 b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 m\u00e0 c\u00e1c ch\u00e0ng trai tr\u00ecnh di\u1ec5n n\u0103m ngo\u00e1i kh\u00f4ng h\u1ec1 d\u1ec5 d\u00e0ng. C\u00f3 r\u1ea5t nhi\u1ec1u c\u00f4ng \u0111o\u1ea1n \u0111\u1ec3 s\u1ea3n xu\u1ea5t nh\u1eefng tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u nh\u01b0 v\u1eady. Ch\u00fang t\u00f4i \u0111ang h\u01b0\u1edbng t\u1edbi \u0111i\u1ec1u \u0111\u00f3 m\u1ed9t l\u1ea7n n\u1eefa. \u0110\u1eebng qu\u00ean, nh\u1eefng \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng kh\u00e1c c\u0169ng t\u0103ng c\u01b0\u1eddng l\u1ef1c l\u01b0\u1ee3ng v\u00e0 h\u1ecd c\u0169ng ch\u1eb3ng h\u1ec1 y\u1ebfu h\u01a1n \u0111\u00e2u.&rdquo;</div>\r\n<div>&nbsp;</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&ldquo;Man City kh\u00f4ng m\u1ea5t b\u1ea5t k\u1ef3 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 n\u00e0o, v\u00ec v\u1eady ngh\u0129a l\u00e0 h\u1ecd s\u1ebd m\u1ea1nh nh\u01b0 n\u0103m ngo\u00e1i c\u1ed9ng th\u00eam Mahrez. Man United c\u0169ng v\u1eady, \u0111i\u1ec1u r\u1ea5t d\u1ec5 hi\u1ec3u. Ch\u00fang t\u00f4i mong \u0111\u1ee3i nhi\u1ec1u h\u01a1n t\u1eeb ch\u00ednh m\u00ecnh, ch\u00fang t\u00f4i s\u1ebd chi\u1ebfn \u0111\u1ea5u cho danh hi\u1ec7u, m\u1ecdi gi\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ea5u. Nh\u01b0ng \u0111i\u1ec1u \u0111\u00f3 kh\u00f4ng c\u00f3 ngh\u0129a t\u00f4i s\u1ebd ng\u1ed3i \u0111\u00e2y, t\u1ef1 tin v\u00e0 n\u00f3i r\u1eb1ng \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng s\u1ebd gi\u00e0nh \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c c\u00fap.&rdquo;<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&ldquo;T\u00f4i \u0111ang \u1edf m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i th\u1ee9 3 v\u00e0 s\u1eb5n s\u00e0ng c\u1ed1ng hi\u1ebfn 100 s\u1ee9c l\u1ef1c c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh. C\u00e1c c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 c\u0169ng v\u1eady, nh\u01b0ng \u0111\u1eebng ng\u1ea1c nhi\u00ean n\u1ebfu ch\u00fang t\u00f4i kh\u00f4ng ch\u01a1i t\u1ed1t trong nh\u1eefng v\u00f2ng \u0111\u1ea7u. T\u00f4i mu\u1ed1n c\u00f3 s\u1ef1 kh\u1edfi \u0111\u1ea7u t\u1ed1t, c\u00f3 s\u1ef1 chu\u1ea9n b\u1ecb t\u1ed1t v\u00e0 h\u01b0\u1edbng \u0111\u1ebfn c\u00e1i k\u1ebft t\u1ed1t \u0111\u1eb9p&rdquo; &ndash; Klopp t\u1ef1 tin gi\u00e0nh danh hi\u1ec7u c\u00f9ng Liverpool.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/karius-thua-nhan-tuong-lai-bat-dinh-sau-khi-liverpool-don-alisson-172-191863.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/20/karius-thua-nhan-tuong-lai-bat-dinh-sau-khi-liverpool-don-alisson.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/karius-thua-nhan-tuong-lai-bat-dinh-sau-khi-liverpool-don-alisson-172-191863.html\">Karius th\u1eeba nh\u1eadn t\u01b0\u01a1ng lai b\u1ea5t \u0111\u1ecbnh sau khi Liverpool \u0111\u00f3n Alisson</span><br>\r\nTh\u1ee7 m\u00f4n ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u0110\u1ee9c ch\u1eafc ch\u1eafn s\u1ebd kh\u00f4ng c\u00f2n \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c tin t\u01b0\u1edfng tr\u1ecdng d\u1ee5ng cho v\u1ecb tr\u00ed s\u1ed1 m\u1ed9t trong khung g\u1ed7 Anfield \u1edf m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i t\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y, b\u1ecf ng\u1ecf kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng ch\u1ee7 \u0111\u1ed9ng ra \u0111i...</div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/klopp-bat-ngo-dam-bao-tuong-lai-cho-phe-pham-cua-liverpool-172-191866.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/19/klopp-bat-ngo-dam-bao-tuong-lai-cho-phe-pham-cua-liverpool.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/klopp-bat-ngo-dam-bao-tuong-lai-cho-phe-pham-cua-liverpool-172-191866.html\">Klopp b\u1ea5t ng\u1edd \u0111\u1ea3m b\u1ea3o t\u01b0\u01a1ng lai cho &ldquo;ph\u1ebf ph\u1ea9m&rdquo; c\u1ee7a Liverpool</span><br>\r\nTi\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o th\u1ea5t s\u1ee7ng Daniel Sturridge \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c m\u1edf \u0111\u01b0\u1eddng \u1edf l\u1ea1i Anfield khi \u0111ang \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c tr\u1ecdng d\u1ee5ng \u1edf chuy\u1ebfn du \u0111\u1ea5u h\u00e8 c\u1ee7a Liverpool.</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Nguy\u1ec7t Anh (TTVN)</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"1562","checkdouble":"191880"},{"date":"08:18 24/07","title":"Enrique c\u1ea7n gi\u00fap \u0110T T\u00e2y Ban Nha v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch EURO 2020","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/10/enrique-can-giup-dt-tay-ban-nha-vo-dich-euro-2020.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Sau m\u1ed9t k\u1ef3 World Cup th\u1ea3m h\u1ea1i v\u1edbi scandal l\u1edbn, B\u00f2 t\u00f3t \u0111\u00e3 quy\u1ebft \u0111\u1ecbnh thay t\u01b0\u1edbng. M\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y, ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o David Villa \u1ee7ng h\u1ed9 HLV Luis Enrique \u0111em l\u1ea1i th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng cho \u0110T.</h2><h2><br>\r\nVilla mu\u1ed1n T\u00e2y Ban Nha l\u00ean ng\u00f4i v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch<br>\r\n&nbsp;</h2>\r\n<div>Tr\u01b0\u1edbc khi World Cup 2018 di\u1ec5n ra 1 ng\u00e0y, \u0110T T\u00e2y Ban Nha ch\u00ednh th\u1ee9c sa th\u1ea3i HLV Julen Lopetegui v\u00e0 b\u1ed5 nhi\u1ec7m Fernando Hierro thay th\u1ebf. Sau gi\u1ea3i, Hierro c\u0169ng r\u1eddi kh\u1ecfi chi\u1ebfc gh\u1ebf n\u00f3ng v\u00e0 nh\u01b0\u1eddng ch\u1ed7 cho Luis Enrique &ndash; c\u1ef1u HLV c\u1ee7a Barca, v\u00e0 t\u1eebng kho\u00e1c \u00e1o c\u1ea3 2 \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng h\u00e0ng \u0111\u1ea7u La Liga khi c\u00f2n thi \u0111\u1ea5u.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">B\u1ecf qua s\u1ef1 th\u1ea5t v\u1ecdng tr\u00ean \u0111\u1ea5t Nga, B\u00f2 t\u00f3t c\u1ea7n ph\u1ea3i th\u1ec3 hi\u1ec7n \u0111\u1eb3ng c\u1ea5p v\u1ed1n c\u00f3 v\u00e0 h\u01b0\u1edbng t\u1edbi ch\u1ee9c v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch EURO 2020. M\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y, ch\u00e2n s\u00fat k\u1ef3 c\u1ef1u David Villa \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 nh\u1eefng l\u1eddi chia s\u1ebb v\u1ec1 Enrique: &ldquo;Th\u00e1ch th\u1ee9c \u0111\u1eb7t ra cho \u00f4ng r\u1ea5t l\u00e0 r\u1ea5t l\u1edbn, b\u1edfi \u0110T \u0111\u00e3 gi\u00e0nh \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c m\u1ecdi danh hi\u1ec7u trong nh\u1eefng gi\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ea5u \u0111\u1ec9nh cao.&rdquo;<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<div style=\"width: 100%;\" class=\"imagecontainer\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"width: 100%;\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"David Villa \u1ee7ng h\u1ed9 HLV Luis Enrique\" title=\"HLV Luis Enrique\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2017/1/23/dai-thang-eibar-hlv-enrique-van-chua-hai-long.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>David Villa \u1ee7ng h\u1ed9 HLV Luis Enrique</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div><br>\r\n&ldquo;T\u00f4i kh\u00f4ng c\u00f3 m\u1eb7t t\u1ea1i World Cup 2018, v\u00ec v\u1eady th\u1eadt kh\u00f3 \u0111\u1ec3 n\u00f3i v\u1ec1 nh\u1eefng g\u00ec \u0111\u00e3 di\u1ec5n ra. Th\u1eadt kh\u00f3 \u0111\u1ec3 nh\u00ecn nh\u1eadn v\u1ea5n \u0111\u1ec1 khi b\u1ea1n kh\u00f4ng t\u1eadn m\u1eaft ch\u1ee9ng ki\u1ebfn. T\u00f4i ngh\u0129 v\u1ec1 b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 nhi\u1ec1u h\u01a1n nh\u1eefng g\u00ec b\u00ean ngo\u00e0i s\u00e2n c\u1ecf. N\u1ebfu b\u1ea1n l\u00e0m \u0111\u00fang, c\u00f3 m\u1ed9t chi\u1ebfn thu\u1eadt t\u1ed1t, b\u1ea1n th\u1eafng. N\u1ebfu kh\u00f4ng, b\u1ea1n th\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i, \u0111\u01a1n gi\u1ea3n l\u00e0 v\u1eady.&rdquo;</div>\r\n<div>&nbsp;</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&ldquo;Khi \u0111\u1ed1i m\u1eb7t v\u1edbi nh\u1eefng \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng c\u00f3 ngu\u1ed3n \u0111\u1ed9ng l\u1ef1c l\u1edbn, b\u1ea1n c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 th\u1ea5y \u0110T Nga c\u00f3 m\u1ed9t k\u1ef3 World Cup tuy\u1ec7t v\u1eddi, nh\u1eefng g\u00ec h\u1ecd th\u1ec3 hi\u1ec7n tr\u01b0\u1edbc Croatia \u1edf v\u00f2ng t\u1ee9 k\u1ebft. \u0110\u00f3 l\u00e0 l\u00fd do h\u1ecd ti\u1ec5n T\u00e2y Ban Nha v\u1ec1 n\u01b0\u1edbc v\u1edbi chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng \u1edf v\u00f2ng 1/8. \u0110\u00f3 l\u00e0 nh\u1eefng g\u00ec b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 di\u1ec5n ra, b\u1ea1n ph\u1ea3i l\u00e0m t\u1ea5t c\u1ea3 nh\u1eefng g\u00ec c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 \u0111\u1ec3 gi\u00e0nh th\u1eafng l\u1ee3i.&rdquo;<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&ldquo;Gi\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ea5u ti\u1ebfp theo s\u1ebd l\u00e0 EURO 2020, v\u00ec v\u1eady \u00f4ng \u1ea5y s\u1ebd ph\u1ea3i l\u1eafp r\u00e1p \u0111\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh \u0111\u1ea1t ch\u1ea5t l\u01b0\u1ee3ng cao nh\u1ea5t, sau \u0111\u00f3 b\u01b0\u1edbc v\u00e0o gi\u1ea3i v\u1edbi nh\u1eefng ng\u00f4i sao xu\u1ea5t s\u1eafc nh\u1ea5t c\u00f3 th\u1ec3. D\u00f9 sao v\u1edbi t\u00e0i n\u0103ng hu\u1ea5n luy\u1ec7n, t\u00f4i hy v\u1ecdng \u00f4ng \u1ea5y s\u1ebd \u0111em l\u1ea1i nh\u1eefng \u0111i\u1ec1u t\u1ed1t nh\u1ea5t cho \u0110T T\u00e2y Ban Nha&rdquo; &ndash; David Villa \u1ee7ng h\u1ed9 HLV Luis Enrique.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;<br>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/bong-da-chau-au/luis-enrique-tu-tin-tai-thiet-tay-ban-nha-184-191508.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/10/luis-enrique-tu-tin-tai-thiet-tay-ban-nha.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/bong-da-chau-au/luis-enrique-tu-tin-tai-thiet-tay-ban-nha-184-191508.html\">Luis Enrique t\u1ef1 tin t\u00e1i thi\u1ebft T\u00e2y Ban Nha</span><br>\r\nT\u00e2n HLV 48 tu\u1ed5i tuy\u00ean b\u1ed1 s\u1eb5n s\u00e0ng cho nh\u1eefng th\u1eed th\u00e1ch tr\u00ean gh\u1ebf n\u00f3ng \u0111\u1ed9i tuy\u1ec3n qu\u1ed1c gia n\u01b0\u1edbc nh\u00e0.</div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/ldbd-tay-ban-nha-nai-ni-pique-dung-chia-tay-dtqg-421-190823.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/6/26/ldbd-tay-ban-nha-nai-ni-pique-dung-chia-tay-dtqg.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/ldbd-tay-ban-nha-nai-ni-pique-dung-chia-tay-dtqg-421-190823.html\">L\u0110B\u0110 T\u00e2y Ban Nha n\u00e0i n\u1ec9 Pique \u0111\u1eebng chia tay \u0110TQG</span><br>\r\nGerard Pique chia tay \u0110T T\u00e2y Ban Nha sau World Cup 2018 l\u00e0 d\u1ef1 \u0111\u1ecbnh c\u1ee7a c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 n\u00e0y, song L\u0110B\u0110 x\u1ee9 s\u1edf B\u00f2 t\u00f3t mu\u1ed1n ng\u00f4i sao c\u1ee7a Barca thay \u0111\u1ed5i quy\u1ebft \u0111\u1ecbnh c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh.</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Nguy\u1ec7t Anh (TTVN)</div>\r\n<br></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"1561","checkdouble":"191881"},{"date":"08:12 24/07","title":"Nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh Cluj vs Malmo 23h00 ng\u00e0y 24/7 (Champions League 2018/19)","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/24/nhan-dinh-cluj-vs-malmo-23h00-ngay-247-champions-league-201819.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Cluj vs Malmo l\u00fac 23h00 ng\u00e0y 24/7 (V\u00f2ng s\u01a1 lo\u1ea1i c\u00fap C1/Champions League 2018/19)): Nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1, \u00fd ki\u1ebfn chuy\u00ean gia, d\u1ef1 \u0111o\u00e1n k\u1ebft qu\u1ea3, ph\u00e2n t\u00edch chuy\u00ean m\u00f4n, c\u00e1c th\u00f4ng tin, th\u1ed1ng k\u00ea b\u00ean l\u1ec1 tr\u01b0\u1edbc tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u.</h2><div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh Cluj vs Malmo 23h00 ng\u00e0y 247 Champions League 201819 h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh Cluj vs Malmo 23h00 ng\u00e0y 247 Champions League 201819 h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/24/Cluj-vs-Malmo.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">Cluj vs Malmo</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: left;\">\r\n<h2 style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: Arial, Verdana, sans-serif; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: 2; text-align: left; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/nhan-dinh-bong-da-c344-p1.html\" target=\"_blank\">Nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1</span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span> </span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span>Cluj vs Malmo: 0-1<br>\r\n</span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></h2>\r\nM\u00f9a tr\u01b0\u1edbc r\u1ea5t th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng v\u1edbi CFR Cluj khi h\u1ecd \u0111\u00e3 gi\u00e0nh ch\u1ee9c V\u0110QG Romania sau 6 n\u0103m. Nh\u1edd v\u1eady, th\u1ea7y tr\u00f2 Edward Iordanescu \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c tham d\u1ef1 Champions League 2018/19 t\u1eeb v\u00f2ng s\u01a1 lo\u1ea1i th\u1ee9 2 v\u00e0 \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7 c\u1ee7a Cluj l\u00e0 Malmo, \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng c\u1ee7a Th\u1ee5y \u0110i\u1ebbn ph\u1ea3i b\u1eaft \u0111\u1ea7u t\u1eeb v\u00f2ng s\u01a1 lo\u1ea1i th\u1ee9 nh\u1ea5t.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nDo c\u00f3 \u01b0u th\u1ebf s\u00e2n nh\u00e0 \u1edf tr\u1eadn l\u01b0\u1ee3t \u0111i n\u00ean CFR Cluj \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111\u00e1nh gi\u00e1 cao h\u01a1n. Song tr\u00ean th\u1ef1c t\u1ebf, sau 6 n\u0103m CFR Cluj m\u1edbi \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c tr\u1edf l\u1ea1i Champions League (m\u00f9a 2012-13 h\u1ecd t\u1eebng g\u00f3p m\u1eb7t \u1edf t\u1eadn v\u00f2ng b\u1ea3ng). L\u1ea7n g\u1ea7n nh\u1ea5t \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng Romania tham d\u1ef1 c\u00fap ch\u00e2u \u00c2u l\u00e0 2014-15 (Europa League) nh\u01b0ng ph\u1ea3i d\u1eebng b\u01b0\u1edbc \u1edf v\u00f2ng s\u01a1 lo\u1ea1i th\u1ee9 3.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nX\u00e9t kinh nghi\u1ec7m d\u1ef1 c\u00fap ch\u00e2u \u00c2u trong nh\u1eefng m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i g\u1ea7n \u0111\u00e2y, Malmo r\u00f5 r\u00e0ng nh\u1ec9nh h\u01a1n. M\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i 2015-16, Nh\u00e0 \u0110KV\u0110 Th\u1ee5y \u0110i\u1ec3n t\u1eebng g\u00f3p m\u1eb7t \u1edf v\u00f2ng \u0111\u1ea5u b\u1ea3ng Champions League.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nTh\u1eddi \u0111i\u1ec3m n\u00e0y, Malmo \u0111\u00e3 l\u1ea5y l\u1ea1i phong \u0111\u1ed9 sau m\u00e0n kh\u1edfi \u0111\u1ea7u kh\u00f4ng t\u1ed1t \u1edf gi\u1ea3i qu\u1ed1c n\u1ed9i. 7 tr\u1eadn ch\u00ednh th\u1ee9c g\u1ea7n nh\u1ea5t tr\u00ean m\u1ecdi \u0111\u1ea5u tr\u01b0\u1eddng, th\u1ea7y tr\u00f2 Uwe R\u00f6sler b\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i (th\u1eafng 5), trong \u0111\u00f3 c\u00f3 2 chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng v\u1edbi t\u1ed5ng t\u1ef7 s\u1ed1 5-0 \u1edf v\u00f2ng s\u01a1 lo\u1ea1i th\u1ee9 nh\u1ea5t Champions League.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nTrong khi \u0111\u00f3, CFR Cluj v\u1eeba c\u00f3 tr\u1eadn m\u1edf m\u00e0n gi\u1ea3i V\u0110QG Romania m\u00f9a b\u00f3ng m\u1edbi 2018-19 kh\u00f4ng th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng khi b\u1ecb c\u1ea7m h\u00f2a 1-1 t\u1ea1i s\u00e2n nh\u00e0. T\u00ednh c\u1ea3 lo\u1ea1t tr\u1eadn giao h\u1eefu tr\u01b0\u1edbc m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i, th\u1ea7y tr\u00f2 tr\u00f2 Edward Iordanescu ch\u1ec9 th\u1eafng 2/6 tr\u1eadn g\u1ea7n nh\u1ea5t. <br>\r\n<br>\r\nTr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u n\u00e0y c\u0169ng kh\u00f4ng h\u1ee9a h\u1eb9n k\u1ecbch b\u1ea3n t\u01b0ng b\u1eebng b\u1edfi CFR Cluj \u0111ang th\u1ec3 hi\u1ec7n kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng t\u1ea5n c\u00f4ng kh\u00e1 ngh\u00e8o n\u00e0n khi 5/6 tr\u1eadn g\u1ea7n nh\u1ea5t c\u1ee7a h\u1ecd ch\u1ec9 c\u00f3 t\u1ed1i \u0111a 2 b\u00e0n th\u1eafng.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n\u0110\u1ed8I H\u00ccNH D\u1ef0 KI\u1ebeN<br>\r\n+ CFR Cluj (4-2-3-1): Arlauskis - Manea, Paulo Vinicius, Muresan, Camora - Djokovic, Hoban - Deac, Culio, Omarani - Tucudean.<br>\r\n+ Malmo (4-4-2): Dahlin - Vindheim, Nielsen, Brorsson, Safari - Lewicki, Bachirou - Christiansen, Rieks - Traustason, Strandberg.</div>\r\n<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<br></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"1560","checkdouble":"191882"},{"date":"08:54 24/07","title":"Ch\u1ee7 t\u1ecbch H\u1eefu Th\u1eafng n\u00f3i g\u00ec khi S\u1ea7m Ng\u1ecdc \u0110\u1ee9c ph\u1ea1m l\u1ed7i th\u00f4 b\u1ea1o?","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/5/28/chu-tich-huu-thang-noi-gi-khi-sam-ngoc-duc-pham-loi-tho-bao.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Tr\u01b0\u1edbc vi\u1ec7c c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 c\u1ee7a \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng l\u00e0 S\u1ea7m Ng\u1ecdc \u0110\u1ee9c ph\u1ea1m l\u1ed7i th\u00f4 b\u1ea1o trong tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u v\u1edbi Than Qu\u1ea3ng Ninh cu\u1ed1i tu\u1ea7n qua, ch\u1ee7 t\u1ecbch CLB TP.HCM Nguy\u1ec5n H\u1eefu Th\u1eafng \u0111\u00e3 l\u00ean ti\u1ebfng n\u00f3i v\u1ec1 chuy\u1ec7n n\u00e0y.</h2><p style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Nh\u01b0 nh\u1eefng th\u00f4ng tin \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c Bongda24h \u0111\u0103ng t\u1ea3i, trong tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u gi\u1eefa CLB TP.HCM vs Than Qu\u1ea3ng Ninh thu\u1ed9c v\u00f2ng 20 V-League 2018 di\u1ec5n ra chi\u1ec1u 23/7, khi t\u1ec9 s\u1ed1 \u0111ang l\u00e0 2-1 nghi\u00eang v\u1ec1 \u0111\u1ed9i ch\u1ee7 nh\u00e0 th\u00ec h\u1eadu v\u1ec7 S\u1ea7m Ng\u1ecdc \u0110\u1ee9c \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 pha \u0111\u1ea1p th\u1eb3ng v\u00e0o ng\u01b0\u1eddi c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 \u0111\u1ed9i kh\u00e1ch Than Qu\u1ea3ng Ninh \u1edf ph\u00fat 84.</p>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><p style=\"text-align: justify;\">V\u00e0 tr\u1ecdng t\u00e0i ch\u00ednh Tr\u1ea7n V\u0103n L\u1eadp \u1edf m\u1ed9t c\u1ef1 ly kh\u00f4ng xa \u0111\u00e3 quan s\u00e1t t\u00ecnh hu\u1ed1ng n\u00e0y v\u00e0 kh\u00f4ng m\u1ed9t ch\u00fat do d\u1ef1 \u0111\u00e3 r\u00fat th\u1ebb \u0111\u1ecf tr\u1ef1c ti\u1ebfp v\u1edbi h\u1eadu v\u1ec7 \u0111\u1ed9i ch\u1ee7 s\u00e2n Th\u1ed1ng Nh\u1ea5t.</p>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Tan Chu tich Nguyen Huu Thang khong dat muc tieu vao top 3 nhu Le Cong Vinh.\" title=\"T\u00e2n Ch\u1ee7 t\u1ecbch Nguy\u1ec5n H\u1eefu Th\u1eafng kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u1eb7t m\u1ee5c ti\u00eau v\u00e0o top 3 nh\u01b0 L\u00ea C\u00f4ng Vinh.\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/5/28/chu-tich-huu-thang-noi-gi-khi-sam-ngoc-duc-pham-loi-tho-bao.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td><em>Ch\u1ee7 t\u1ecbch Nguy\u1ec5n H\u1eefu Th\u1eafng x\u00e1c nh\u1eadn h\u1eadu v\u1ec7 S\u1ea7m Ng\u1ecdc \u0110\u1ee9c t\u1ecf ra \u00e2n h\u1eadn sau sai l\u1ea7m v\u1eeba qua</em></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Sau tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u n\u00e0y, S\u1ea7m Ng\u1ecdc \u0110\u1ee9c \u0111\u00e3 b\u1ecb l\u00ean \u00e1n b\u1edfi h\u00e0nh vi v\u00e0o b\u00f3ng phi th\u1ec3 thao v\u1edbi c\u00e1c \u0111\u1ed3ng nghi\u1ec7p. Tr\u01b0\u1edbc t\u00ecnh h\u00ecnh n\u00e0y, ch\u1ee7 t\u1ecbch CLB TP.HCM \u00f4ng Nguy\u1ec5n H\u1eefu Th\u1eafng \u0111\u00e3 l\u00ean ti\u1ebfng n\u00f3i \u0111\u1ee1 cho c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 x\u1ee9 Ngh\u1ec7.</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">&ldquo;H\u1ebft tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u, v\u00e0o trong ph\u00f2ng thay \u0111\u1ed3, S\u1ea7m Ng\u1ecdc \u0110\u1ee9c kh\u00f4ng k\u00ecm \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c c\u1ea3m x\u00fac v\u00e0 b\u1eadt kh\u00f3c. T\u00f4i n\u00f3i th\u1ee9 nh\u1ea5t \u0111\u00f3 l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t b\u00e0i h\u1ecdc s\u00e2u s\u1eafc, ph\u1ea3i r\u00fat kinh nghi\u1ec7m. L\u00e0 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 chuy\u00ean nghi\u1ec7p, \u0110\u1ee9c ph\u1ea3i gi\u1eef b\u00ecnh t\u0129nh tr\u00ean s\u00e2n b\u00f3ng.</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">C\u00f3 th\u1ec3 v\u00e0o b\u00f3ng quy\u1ebft li\u1ec7t, v\u00ec l\u00e0 m\u00f4n \u0111\u1ed1i kh\u00e1ng nh\u01b0ng \u0111\u1ed9ng t\u00e1c ph\u1ea3n c\u1ea3m nh\u01b0 th\u1ebf th\u00ec kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c, ph\u1ea3i lo\u1ea1i b\u1ecf b\u1eb1ng m\u1ecdi gi\u00e1. S\u1ef1 vi\u1ec7c c\u0169ng \u0111\u00e3 qua r\u1ed3i, n\u1ebfu Th\u1ebf H\u01b0ng b\u1ecb \u0111au n\u1eb7ng ch\u1eafc c\u1ea3m gi\u00e1c t\u1ed9i l\u1ed7i c\u1ee7a ch\u00e1u s\u1ebd c\u00e0ng n\u1eb7ng n\u1ec1 h\u01a1n.</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Ng\u1ecdc \u0110\u1ee9c \u0111\u00e3 xin l\u1ed7i Th\u1ebf H\u01b0ng v\u00e0 BHL T.Qu\u1ea3ng Ninh. Ch\u00e1u bi\u1ebft l\u1ed7i m\u00ecnh r\u1ea5t n\u1eb7ng v\u00e0 m\u1ecdi tr\u00ecnh b\u00e0y l\u00fac n\u00e0y \u0111\u1ec1u l\u00e0 th\u1eeba. Ch\u00fang t\u00f4i r\u1ea5t ti\u1ebfc, xin l\u1ed7i c\u00e1 nh\u00e2n Th\u1ebf H\u01b0ng, CLB T.Qu\u1ea3ng Ninh c\u0169ng nh\u01b0 ng\u01b0\u1eddi h\u00e2m m\u1ed9 v\u1ec1 s\u1ef1 c\u1ed1 ph\u1ea3n c\u1ea3m n\u00e0y&rdquo;, Ch\u1ee7 t\u1ecbch CLB TP.HCM Nguy\u1ec5n H\u1eefu Th\u1eafng ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u.</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">V\u1ec1 ph\u1ea7n m\u00ecnh, h\u1eadu v\u1ec7 S\u1ea7m Ng\u1ecdc \u0110\u1ee9c c\u0169ng cho bi\u1ebft anh \u0111\u00e3 g\u1eedi l\u1eddi xin l\u1ed7i t\u1edbi c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 Th\u1ebf H\u01b0ng c\u1ee7a CLB T.Qu\u1ea3ng Ninh. C\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi Ngh\u1ec7 An c\u0169ng cho bi\u1ebft s\u1ebd ch\u1ea5p nh\u1eadn m\u1ecdi \u00e1n ph\u1ea1t \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111\u01b0a ra t\u1eeb ph\u00eda VFF nh\u01b0ng hy v\u1ecdng s\u1ebd c\u00f3 c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i \u0111\u1ec3 s\u1eeda ch\u1eefa sai l\u1ea7m sau \u0111\u00f3.</p>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/hlv-miura-noi-gi-khi-chung-kien-hoc-tro-da-tho-bao-168-191820.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/6/24/hlv-miura-noi-gi-khi-chung-kien-hoc-tro-da-tho-bao.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/hlv-miura-noi-gi-khi-chung-kien-hoc-tro-da-tho-bao-168-191820.html\">HLV Miura n\u00f3i g\u00ec khi h\u1ecdc tr\u00f2 b\u1ecb \u0111u\u1ed5i v\u00ec thi \u0111\u1ea5u th\u00f4 b\u1ea1o?</span><br>\r\nTr\u01b0\u1edbc vi\u1ec7c h\u1eadu v\u1ec7 S\u1ea7m Ng\u1ecdc \u0110\u1ee9c b\u1ecb \u0111u\u1ed5i kh\u1ecfi s\u00e2n v\u00ec l\u1ed7i v\u00e0o b\u00f3ng th\u00f4 b\u1ea1o, HLV Toshiya Miura \u0111\u00e3 l\u00ean ti\u1ebfng b\u1ea3o v\u1ec7 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh.</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Minh Long (TTVN)</p></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"1559","checkdouble":"191885"},{"date":"08:26 24/07","title":"Nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh Legia Warszawa vs Trnava 02h00 ng\u00e0y 25/7 (Champions League 2018/19)","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/24/nhan-dinh-legia-warszawa-vs-trnava-02h00-ngay-257-champions-league-201819.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Legia Warszawa vs Trnava l\u00fac 02h00 ng\u00e0y 25/7 (V\u00f2ng s\u01a1 lo\u1ea1i c\u00fap C1/Champions League 2018/19)): Nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1, \u00fd ki\u1ebfn chuy\u00ean gia, d\u1ef1 \u0111o\u00e1n k\u1ebft qu\u1ea3, ph\u00e2n t\u00edch chuy\u00ean m\u00f4n, c\u00e1c th\u00f4ng tin, th\u1ed1ng k\u00ea b\u00ean l\u1ec1 tr\u01b0\u1edbc tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u.</h2><div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh Legia Warszawa vs Trnava 02h00 ng\u00e0y 257 c\u00fap C1 201819 h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh Legia Warszawa vs Trnava 02h00 ng\u00e0y 257 c\u00fap C1 201819 h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/24/Legia-Warszawa-vs-Trnava.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">Legia Warszawa vs Trnava</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n<h2 style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: Arial, Verdana, sans-serif; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: 2; text-align: left; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/nhan-dinh-bong-da-c344-p1.html\" target=\"_blank\">Nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1</span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span> </span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span>Legia Warszawa vs Trnava: 3-1<br>\r\n</span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></h2>\r\n\u1ede v\u00f2ng s\u01a1 lo\u1ea1i th\u1ee9 nh\u1ea5t, Legia Warszawa \u0111\u00e3 d\u1ec5 d\u00e0ng v\u01b0\u1ee3t qua Cork City, nh\u00e0 v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch CH Ireland, v\u1edbi t\u1ed5ng t\u1ef7 s\u1ed1 4-0 (1-0 v\u00e0 3-0). Tr\u00ean s\u00e2n nh\u00e0, Legia Warszawa \u0111ang l\u00e0 \u0111\u1ecba ch\u1ec9 kh\u00e1 tin c\u1eady khi th\u1eafng 6/8 tr\u1eadn v\u1eeba qua theo TLCA.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nGi\u1ed1ng nh\u01b0 \u0111\u1ea1i di\u1ec7n Ba Lan, Trnava c\u0169ng b\u1eaft \u0111\u1ea7u xu\u1ea5t ph\u00e1t t\u1eeb v\u00f2ng s\u01a1 lo\u1ea1i th\u1ee9 nh\u1ea5t. Th\u1ebf nh\u01b0ng, h\u00e0nh tr\u00ecnh chinh ph\u1ee5c t\u1ea5m v\u00e9 th\u00f4ng h\u00e0nh v\u00e0o v\u00f2ng s\u01a1 lo\u1ea1i th\u1ee9 2 c\u1ee7a \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng CH Czech g\u1eadp gh\u1ec1nh h\u01a1n nhi\u1ec1u. Tr\u01b0\u1edbc \u0111\u1ea1i di\u1ec7n c\u1ee7a Bosnia - Zrinjski Mostar, Trnava ch\u1ec9 th\u1eafng v\u1edbi t\u1ed5ng t\u1ef7 s\u1ed1 2-1.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nTr\u00ean s\u00e2n kh\u00e1ch, Trnava \u0111ang thi \u0111\u1ea5u kh\u00f4ng t\u1ed1t khi 7 chuy\u1ebfn h\u00e0nh qu\u00e2n g\u1ea7n \u0111\u00e2y h\u1ecd kh\u00f4ng th\u1eafng (thua 4). D\u01b0\u1edbi g\u00f3c \u0111\u1ed9 TLCA, \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng d\u01b0\u1edbi quy\u1ec1n HLV Radoslav L\u00e1tal ch\u1ec9 2 l\u1ea7n v\u01b0\u1ee3t r\u00e0o th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng (thua 4).<br>\r\n<br>\r\n\u0110\u00f3 l\u00e0 l\u00fd do gi\u1ea3i th\u00edch v\u00ec sao Legia Warszawa \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111\u00e1nh gi\u00e1 r\u1ea5t cao v\u00e0o r\u1ea1ng s\u00e1ng mai. S\u1ebd kh\u00f4ng ng\u1ea1c nhi\u00ean n\u1ebfu Legia Warszawa t\u1ea1o \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c l\u1ee3i th\u1ebf \u0111\u00e1ng k\u1ec3 tr\u01b0\u1edbc tr\u1eadn l\u01b0\u1ee3t v\u1ec1.\u00a0 <br>\r\n<br>\r\nTH\u00c0NH T\u00cdCH \u0110\u1ed0I \u0110\u1ea6U<br>\r\n- Hai \u0111\u1ed9i \u0111\u00e3 g\u1eb7p nhau t\u1ed5ng c\u1ed9ng 1 tr\u1eadn, Legia Warszawa th\u1eafng 1, h\u00f2a 0, thua 0.<br>\r\n- Tr\u00ean s\u00e2n c\u1ee7a Legia Warszawa, 2 \u0111\u1ed9i ch\u01b0a t\u1eebng g\u1eb7p nhau. <br>\r\n<br></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"1558","checkdouble":"191886"},{"date":"08:54 24/07","title":"Leroy Sane n\u00f3i g\u00ec v\u1ec1 \"bom t\u1ea5n\" Mahrez?","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/original/2018/7/22/leroy-sane-noi-gi-ve-bom-tan-mahrez.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Leroy Sane ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u v\u1ec1 Riyad Mahrez, ng\u00f4i sao ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u0110\u1ee9c kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh s\u1ef1 c\u00f3 m\u1eb7t c\u1ee7a c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 27 tu\u1ed5i s\u1ebd gi\u00fap \u0111\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh Man City m\u1ea1nh h\u01a1n r\u1ea5t nhi\u1ec1u.\r\n</h2><h2 style=\"text-align: justify;\">Sane \u0111\u00e1nh gi\u00e1 cao Mahrez</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nC\u00e1ch \u0111\u00e2y kh\u00f4ng l\u00e2u, <span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/bong-da-anh/man-city-chieu-mo-thanh-cong-mahrez-172-190895.html\" target=\"_blank\">Man City mua Riyad Mahrez</span> th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng v\u1edbi gi\u00e1 60 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng. Tr\u01b0\u1edbc \u0111\u00f3, v\u00e0o th\u00e1ng 1 v\u1eeba qua \u0111\u1ed9i ch\u1ee7 s\u00e2n Etihad \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u00e1nh ti\u1ebfng mu\u1ed1n c\u00f3 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 27 tu\u1ed5i nh\u01b0ng kh\u00f4ng th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng. Ngay khi TTCN H\u00e8 2018 m\u1edf c\u1eeda Man xanh \u0111\u00e3 n\u1ed1i l\u1ea1i \u0111\u00e0m ph\u00e1n v\u00e0 c\u00f3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111i\u1ec1u m\u00ecnh c\u1ea7n.<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Leroy Sane ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u v\u1ec1 Riyad Mahrez h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Leroy Sane ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u v\u1ec1 Riyad Mahrez h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/22/leroy-sane-noi-gi-ve-bom-tan-mahrez.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Sane \u0111\u00e1nh gi\u00e1 cao t\u00e0i n\u0103ng c\u1ee7a Mahrez</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nMahrez l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t trong nh\u1eefng c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 quan tr\u1ecdng nh\u1ea5t c\u1ee7a Leicester trong nh\u1eefng n\u0103m g\u1ea7n \u0111\u00e2y, m\u00f9a v\u1eeba r\u1ed3i anh ghi t\u1edbi 12 b\u00e0n th\u1eafng c\u00f9ng 10 ki\u1ebfn t\u1ea1o. Ng\u00f4i sao ng\u01b0\u1eddi Algeria r\u1ea5t \u0111a n\u0103ng khi c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 thi \u0111\u1ea5u \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u1edf nhi\u1ec1u v\u1ecb tr\u00ed tr\u00ean h\u00e0ng c\u00f4ng.</div>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nLeroy Sane ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u v\u1ec1 Riyad Mahrez, ng\u00f4i sao ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u0110\u1ee9c \u0111\u00e1nh gi\u00e1 cao t\u00e0i n\u0103ng c\u1ee7a c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 sinh n\u0103m 1991.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\n\u201cAnh \u1ea5y l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t trong nh\u1eefng c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 t\u1ea5n c\u00f4ng h\u00e0ng \u0111\u1ea7u gi\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ea5u, Mahrez th\u1ef1c s\u1ef1 t\u00e0i n\u0103ng. Anh \u1ea5y s\u1edf h\u1eefu nh\u1eefng t\u1ed1 ch\u1ea5t c\u1ee7a m\u1ed9t c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 h\u00e0ng \u0111\u1ea7u, anh \u1ea5y c\u00f3 t\u1ed1c \u0111\u1ed9, k\u1ef9 thu\u1eadt, kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng qua ng\u01b0\u1eddi v\u00e0 d\u1ee9t \u0111i\u1ec3m t\u1ed1t, t\u00f4i h\u1ea1nh ph\u00fac khi \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c ch\u01a1i b\u00ean c\u1ea1nh Mahrez\u201d.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\n\u201cS\u1ef1 c\u00f3 m\u1eb7t c\u1ee7a anh \u1ea5y s\u1ebd gi\u00fap Man City m\u1ea1nh h\u01a1n r\u1ea5t nhi\u1ec1u, v\u1edbi vi\u1ec7c \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 kinh nghi\u1ec7m thi \u0111\u1ea5u \u1edf Ngo\u1ea1i h\u1ea1ng Anh t\u00f4i tin anh \u1ea5y s\u1ebd nhanh ch\u00f3ng h\u00f2a nh\u1eadp\u201d.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u00a0</div>\r\n<h2>Sane tin Mahrez s\u1ebd khi\u1ebfn cu\u1ed9c c\u1ea1nh tranh v\u1ecb tr\u00ed tr\u1edf n\u00ean kh\u1ed1c li\u1ec7t</h2>\r\n<h2>\u00a0</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">V\u1edbi s\u1ef1 c\u00f3 m\u1eb7t c\u1ee7a Mahrez, cu\u1ed9c c\u1ea1nh tranh v\u1ecb tr\u00ed t\u1ea1i s\u00e2n Etihad s\u1ebd di\u1ec5n ra th\u1ef1c s\u1ef1 kh\u1ed1c li\u1ec7t. Tuy nhi\u00ean, Sane tin r\u1eb1ng s\u1ef1 c\u1ea1nh tranh t\u1ed1t cho Man City.<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Mahrez toi Man City\" title=\"Mahrez toi Man City\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/21/guardiola-phan-tich-cac-sao-mai-man-city-trong-tran-thua-dortmund.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Mahrez s\u1ebd khi\u1ebfn cu\u1ed9c c\u1ea1nh tranh v\u1ecb tr\u00ed \u1edf Man City tr\u1edf n\u00ean kh\u1ed1c li\u1ec7t</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n\u201cV\u1edbi s\u1ef1 c\u00f3 m\u1eb7t c\u1ee7a Mahrez, ch\u1eafc ch\u1eafn cu\u1ed9c c\u1ea1nh tranh v\u1ecb tr\u00ed s\u1ebd kh\u1ed1c li\u1ec7t h\u01a1n \u1edf m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i t\u1edbi. Tuy nhi\u00ean, \u00e1p l\u1ef1c khi\u1ebfn m\u1ecdi c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 \u0111\u1ec1u ph\u1ea3i ch\u01a1i c\u1ed1 g\u1eafng h\u01a1n, \u0111i\u1ec1u \u0111\u00f3 t\u1ed1t cho \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng. T\u00f4i tin Man City m\u1ea1nh h\u01a1n \u1edf m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i t\u1edbi\u201d.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\n\u201cM\u00f9a tr\u01b0\u1edbc, s\u1ef1 c\u1ea1nh tranh v\u1ecb tr\u00ed bu\u1ed9c Bernardo Silva ph\u1ea3i ph\u00f4 di\u1ec5n nh\u1eefng g\u00ec l\u00e0 t\u1ed1t nh\u1ea5t c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh, anh \u1ea5y \u0111\u00e3 ch\u01a1i r\u1ea5t t\u1ed1t khi \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c trao c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i. M\u00f9a t\u1edbi, anh \u1ea5y s\u1ebd ph\u1ea3i thi \u0111\u1ea5u t\u1ed1t h\u01a1n n\u1eefa n\u1ebfu mu\u1ed1n \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c ra s\u00e2n th\u01b0\u1eddng xuy\u00ean\u201d.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nV\u01b0\u01a1ng Ng\u00e2n (TTVN)</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u00a0</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"1557","checkdouble":"191887"},{"date":"03:12 24/07","title":"Klopp t\u1ecf l\u00f2ng \"th\u01b0\u01a1ng h\u1ea1i\" Tottenham","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/9/klopp-to-long-thuong-hai-tottenham.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Th\u1ea5u hi\u1ec3u n\u1ed7i kh\u1ed1n kh\u00f3 c\u1ee7a Liverpool v\u1edbi t\u00ecnh h\u00ecnh s\u1ee9t m\u1ebb l\u1ef1c l\u01b0\u1ee3ng hi\u1ec7n t\u1ea1i sau k\u1ef3 World Cup 2018, HLV ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u0110\u1ee9c c\u00e0ng th\u1ea5y c\u1ea3m th\u00f4ng cho Tottenham.</h2><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">Liverpool \u0111ang tham gia v\u00e0o chuy\u1ebfn du \u0111\u1ea5u h\u00e8 tr\u00ean \u0111\u1ea5t M\u1ef9 v\u1edbi n\u00f2ng c\u1ed1t ch\u1ee7 y\u1ebfu l\u00e0 c\u00e1c c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 tr\u1ebb \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111\u00f4n l\u00ean t\u1eeb \u0111\u1ed9i d\u1ef1 b\u1ecb, khi c\u00e1c tr\u1ee5 c\u1ed9t v\u1eabn \u0111ang trong qu\u00e1 tr\u00ecnh ngh\u1ec9 ng\u01a1i sau k\u1ef3 World Cup 2018.</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\"><o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">Th\u1eddi gian chu\u1ea9n b\u1ecb cho m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i m\u1edbi th\u1ef1c s\u1ef1 kh\u00f4ng nhi\u1ec1u, th\u1eadm ch\u00ed nhi\u1ec1u ng\u00f4i sao \u0111\u1ee9ng tr\u01b0\u1edbc nguy c\u01a1 v\u1eafng m\u1eb7t ngay c\u1ea3 khi Premier League \u0111\u00e3 ch\u00ednh th\u1ee9c kh\u1edfi tranh. <o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"HLV Klopp n\u00f3i v\u1ec1 Tottenham v\u1edbi s\u1ef1 th\u01b0\u01a1ng h\u1ea1i cho l\u1ef1c l\u01b0\u1ee3ng s\u1ee9t m\u1ebb h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"HLV Klopp n\u00f3i v\u1ec1 Tottenham v\u1edbi s\u1ef1 th\u01b0\u01a1ng h\u1ea1i cho l\u1ef1c l\u01b0\u1ee3ng s\u1ee9t m\u1ebb h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/9/klopp-to-long-thuong-hai-tottenham.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\u0110\u00f3ng g\u00f3p nhi\u1ec1u c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 nh\u1ea5t \u1edf b\u00e1n k\u1ebft World Cup 2018, Tottenham hi\u1ec3n nhi\u00ean s\u1ee9t m\u1ebb l\u1ef1c l\u01b0\u1ee3ng nghi\u00eam tr\u1ecdng nh\u1ea5t tr\u01b0\u1edbc th\u1ec1m m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i m\u1edbi</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">Th\u1ea5u hi\u1ec3u n\u1ed7i kh\u1ed1n kh\u00f3 c\u1ee7a Liverpool v\u1edbi t\u00ecnh h\u00ecnh s\u1ee9t m\u1ebb l\u1ef1c l\u01b0\u1ee3ng hi\u1ec7n t\u1ea1i, HLV Jurgen Klopp c\u00e0ng th\u1ea5y c\u1ea3m th\u00f4ng cho Tottenham, \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00f3ng g\u00f3p nhi\u1ec1u c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 nh\u1ea5t \u1edf v\u00f2ng b\u00e1n k\u1ebft v\u1eeba r\u1ed3i v\u1edbi 9 ng\u01b0\u1eddi, hi\u1ec3n nhi\u00ean c\u0169ng \u0111ang ph\u1ea3i ch\u1ecbu thi\u1ec7t th\u00f2i nh\u1ea5t.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">Qua \u0111\u00e2y, nh\u00e0 c\u1ea7m qu\u00e2n ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u0110\u1ee9c c\u0169ng k\u00eau g\u1ecdi c\u00e1c c\u01a1 quan \u0111i\u1ec1u h\u00e0nh nh\u01b0 UEFA c\u00e2n nh\u1eafc l\u1ea1i vi\u1ec7c s\u1eafp x\u1ebfp l\u1ecbch thi \u0111\u1ea5u qu\u1ed1c t\u1ebf sao cho h\u1ee3p l\u00fd v\u00e0 ph\u00f9 h\u1ee3p h\u01a1n v\u1edbi th\u1ec3 tr\u1ea1ng ch\u1ec9 c\u00f3 gi\u1edbi h\u1ea1n c\u1ee7a c\u00e1c c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7. HLV Klopp n\u00f3i v\u1ec1 Tottenham cho bi\u1ebft:<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">\u201cGi\u1edd th\u00ec ch\u00fang ta chu\u1ea9n b\u1ecb c\u00f3 Nations League (gi\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ea5u giao h\u1eefu c\u1ea5p \u0111\u1ed9 \u0110TQG nh\u01b0ng l\u1ea1i c\u00f3 h\u1ec7 th\u1ed1ng t\u00ednh \u0111i\u1ec3m \u0111\u1ec3 ph\u00e2n h\u1ea1t gi\u1ed1ng cho c\u00e1c chi\u1ebfn d\u1ecbch v\u00f2ng lo\u1ea1i), t\u1ee9c l\u00e0 c\u00e1c c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 g\u1ea7n nh\u01b0 s\u1ebd ph\u1ea3i l\u00ean tuy\u1ec3n tr\u1edf l\u1ea1i ch\u1ec9 sau ch\u01b0a \u0111\u1ea7y hai th\u00e1ng sau World Cup.\u201d<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">\u201cTh\u1eadt \u0111i\u00ean r\u1ed3, v\u00e0 \u0111\u1ea5y l\u00e0 ch\u00fang t\u00f4i m\u1edbi ch\u1ec9 c\u00f3 4 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 v\u01b0\u1edbng m\u1eafc nh\u01b0 th\u1ebf n\u00e0y. Tr\u00f4ng sang Tottenham v\u1edbi 9 ng\u01b0\u1eddi, t\u00f4i kh\u00f4ng hi\u1ec3u h\u1ecd s\u1ebd c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 x\u1eed tr\u00ed ra sao n\u1eefa. C\u00e1c c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 th\u00ec b\u1eaft bu\u1ed9c v\u1eabn ph\u1ea3i c\u1ea7n m\u1ed9t k\u1ef3 ngh\u1ec9 ng\u01a1i tho\u1ea3i m\u00e1i tr\u01b0\u1edbc khi b\u01b0\u1edbc v\u00e0o m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i m\u1edbi.\u201d<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/goc-nhin-vi-hien-tai-va-tuong-lai-tottenham-hay-vo-dich-world-cup-421-190976.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/11/goc-nhin-vi-hien-tai-va-tuong-lai-tottenham-hay-vo-dich-world-cup.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/goc-nhin-vi-hien-tai-va-tuong-lai-tottenham-hay-vo-dich-world-cup-421-190976.html\">G\u00f3c nh\u00ecn: V\u00ec hi\u1ec7n t\u1ea1i v\u00e0 t\u01b0\u01a1ng lai, Tottenham h\u00e3y v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch World Cup!</span><br>\r\nTottenham ch\u00ednh l\u00e0 CLB \u0111\u00f3ng g\u00f3p nhi\u1ec1u c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 nh\u1ea5t \u1edf b\u00e1n k\u1ebft World Cup 2018 v\u00e0 vi\u1ec5n c\u1ea3nh \u00edt nh\u1ea5t m\u1ed9t ng\u00f4i sao Spurs n\u00e2ng cao c\u00fap v\u00e0ng \u0111ang hi\u1ec3n hi\u1ec7n r\u00f5 n\u00e9t, \u00e2u...</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\"><strong>Gia Khoa (TTVN)</strong><o:p></o:p></p></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"1556","checkdouble":"191867"},{"date":"00:36 24/07","title":"Deschamps c\u1ea1n l\u1eddi khi Kante xu\u1ed1ng phong \u0111\u1ed9 \u1edf chung k\u1ebft World Cup","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/16/deschamps-can-loi-khi-kante-xuong-phong-do-o-chung-ket-world-cup.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>H\u1ebft l\u1eddi ng\u1ee3i khen N\u2019Golo Kante nh\u01b0ng HLV Didier Deschamps c\u0169ng kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 gi\u1ea3i th\u00edch n\u1ed5i m\u00e0n tr\u00ecnh di\u1ec5n d\u01b0\u1edbi s\u1ee9c c\u1ee7a ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 ph\u00f2ng ng\u1ef1 Chelsea trong tr\u1eadn Ph\u00e1p vs Croatia chung k\u1ebft World Cup 2018.</h2><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">D\u00f9 sao, m\u00e0n tr\u00ecnh di\u1ec5n th\u1ea5t v\u1ecdng hi\u1ebfm hoi khi \u0111\u1ed1i \u0111\u1ea7u v\u1edbi Qu\u1ea3 B\u00f3ng V\u00e0ng Luka Modric \u0111\u00f3, th\u1eadm ch\u00ed s\u1edbm b\u1ecb thay ra khi th\u1eddi gian thi \u0111\u1ea5u c\u00f2n ch\u01b0a \u0111i\u1ec3m m\u1ed9t gi\u1edd \u0111\u1ed3ng h\u1ed3, c\u0169ng kh\u00f4ng \u1ea3nh h\u01b0\u1edfng nhi\u1ec1u \u0111\u1ebfn ng\u00f4i v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch th\u1ebf gi\u1edbi c\u1ee7a \u0111\u1ed9i tuy\u1ec3n Ph\u00e1p.</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\"><o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">Kh\u00f4ng ai c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 ph\u1ee7 nh\u1eadn t\u00e0i n\u0103ng v\u00e0 t\u1ea7m c\u1ee1 quan tr\u1ecdng c\u1ee7a N\u2019Golo Kante tr\u00ean h\u00e0nh tr\u00ecnh \u0111\u01b0a Les Bleus gi\u00e0nh c\u00fap v\u00e0ng th\u1ee9 hai trong l\u1ecbch s\u1eed, tuy nhi\u00ean t\u1ea5t c\u1ea3 c\u0169ng ph\u1ea3i \u00edt nhi\u1ec1u \u0111\u1eb7t d\u1ea5u h\u1ecfi th\u1eafc m\u1eafc cho phong \u0111\u1ed9 b\u1ea5t ng\u1edd \u0111i xu\u1ed1ng c\u1ee7a ng\u00f4i sao Chelsea thi \u0111\u1ea5u v\u1edbi vai tr\u00f2 \u201cm\u00e1y qu\u00e9t\u201d \u1edf v\u1ecb tr\u00ed ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 ph\u00f2ng ng\u1ef1.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Deschamps vs Kante tr\u1eadn Ph\u00e1p vs Croatia chung k\u1ebft World Cup 2018 h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Deschamps vs Kante tr\u1eadn Ph\u00e1p vs Croatia chung k\u1ebft World Cup 2018 h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/16/deschamps-can-loi-khi-kante-xuong-phong-do-o-chung-ket-world-cup.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 Kante tr\u1eadn Ph\u00e1p vs Croatia chung k\u1ebft World Cup 2018 xu\u1ed1ng phong \u0111\u1ed9 v\u00ec \u0111au d\u1ea1 d\u00e0y</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">Ngay c\u1ea3 HLV Didier Deschamps c\u0169ng c\u1ea1n l\u1eddi gi\u1ea3i th\u00edch lu\u00f4n khi chia s\u1ebb v\u1ec1 c\u1eadu h\u1ecdc tr\u00f2 tr\u1ee5 c\u1ed9t: \u201cT\u00f4i kh\u00f4ng bi\u1ebft chuy\u1ec7n g\u00ec \u0111\u00e3 x\u1ea3y ra v\u1edbi N\u2019Golo trong tr\u1eadn chung k\u1ebft nh\u01b0ng c\u00f3 v\u1ebb n\u00f3 th\u1eadt t\u1ec7 cho c\u1eadu \u1ea5y. D\u00f9 sao, c\u1eadu \u1ea5y v\u1eabn v\u00f4 c\u00f9ng xu\u1ea5t s\u1eafc v\u00e0 kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 \u0111\u00e1nh m\u1ea5t ni\u1ec1m tin c\u1ee7a t\u00f4i ch\u1ec9 v\u00ec m\u1ed9t tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u nh\u01b0 v\u1eady.\u201d<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">\u201cKhi N\u2019Golo r\u1eddi s\u00e2n, t\u00f4i h\u1ecfi th\u0103m li\u1ec7u c\u1eadu \u1ea5y c\u00f3 \u1ed5n kh\u00f4ng. C\u1eadu \u1ea5y ch\u1ec9 tr\u1ea3 l\u1eddi r\u1eb1ng \u0111\u1eebng lo cho m\u00ecnh, h\u00e3y c\u1ee9 t\u1eadp trung v\u00e0o tr\u1eadn chung k\u1ebft. N\u2019Golo l\u00e0 v\u1eady, m\u1ed9t tia n\u1eafng mang y\u00eau th\u01b0\u01a1ng \u0111\u1ebfn t\u1ea5t c\u1ea3 m\u1ecdi ng\u01b0\u1eddi. C\u1eadu \u1ea5y th\u1ef1c s\u1ef1 l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t hi\u1ec7n t\u01b0\u1ee3ng, m\u1ed9t ngu\u1ed3n c\u1ea3m h\u1ee9ng b\u1ea5t ch\u1ea5p s\u1ef1 nh\u1ecf b\u00e9 khi\u00eam nh\u01b0\u1eddng c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh.\u201d<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">\u0110\u01b0\u1ee3c bi\u1ebft, Kante \u0111\u00e3 ph\u1ea3i thi \u0111\u1ea5u v\u1edbi c\u01a1n \u0111au d\u1ea1 d\u00e0y v\u00e0 kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 ch\u1ecbu n\u1ed5i th\u00eam \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c n\u1eefa sau kho\u1ea3ng 10 ph\u00fat hi\u1ec7p hai. Th\u00eam v\u00e0o \u0111\u00f3 b\u00ean c\u1ea1nh th\u1ec3 tr\u1ea1ng, c\u00f3 th\u00f4ng tin cho hay anh trai ng\u00f4i sao Chelsea \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u1ed9t t\u1eed ngay tr\u01b0\u1edbc ng\u00e0y di\u1ec5n ra tr\u1eadn chung k\u1ebft, \u0111\u01b0\u01a1ng nhi\u00ean \u1ea3nh h\u01b0\u1edfng t\u00e2m l\u00fd qu\u00e1 l\u1edbn n\u1ebfu \u0111\u00e2y \u0111\u00fang l\u00e0 s\u1ef1 th\u1eadt.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/qua-de-thuong-kante-ngo-tau-ngai-di-hoi-xin-nho-ban-muon-ho-cup-vang-de-song-ao-421-191369.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/16/qua-de-thuong-kante-ngo-tau-ngai-di-hoi-xin-nho-ban-muon-ho-cup-vang-de-song-ao.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/qua-de-thuong-kante-ngo-tau-ngai-di-hoi-xin-nho-ban-muon-ho-cup-vang-de-song-ao-421-191369.html\">Qu\u00e1 d\u1ec5 th\u01b0\u01a1ng! Kante ng\u1ed1 t\u00e0u ng\u1ea1i \u0111i h\u1ecfi xin, nh\u1edd b\u1ea1n m\u01b0\u1ee3n h\u1ed9 c\u00fap v\u00e0ng \u0111\u1ec3 s\u1ed1ng \u1ea3o</span><br>\r\nTi\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 ph\u00f2ng ng\u1ef1 c\u1ee7a Chelsea ch\u00ednh l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t trong nh\u1eefng c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 quan tr\u1ecdng nh\u1ea5t c\u1ee7a \u0111\u1ed9i tuy\u1ec3n Ph\u00e1p tr\u00ean h\u00e0nh tr\u00ecnh v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch World Cup 2018.</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\"><strong>Gia Khoa (TTVN)</strong><o:p></o:p></p></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"1555","checkdouble":"191868"},{"date":"01:47 24/07","title":"T\u00e2n binh Real Madrid h\u1ea1 m\u1ee5c ti\u00eau v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch Champions League","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2017/5/24/tan-binh-real-madrid-ha-muc-tieu-vo-dich-champions-league.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>D\u01b0\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y l\u00e0 nh\u1eefng tin t\u1ee9c t\u1ed5ng h\u1ee3p \u0111\u00e1ng ch\u00fa \u00fd trong ph\u1ea7n \u0111i\u1ec3m tin b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 tr\u00ean chuy\u00ean trang Bongda24h s\u00e1ng ng\u00e0y 24/7. \r\n</h2><h2><br>\r\n\u0110\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng n\u00e0o s\u1ebd c\u1ea3n b\u01b0\u1edbc Man City \u1edf m\u00f9a sau?<br>\r\n&nbsp;</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">M\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y, ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 Leroy Sane \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u01b0a ra nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh kh\u00e1 b\u1ea5t ng\u1edd, khi cho r\u1eb1ng Chelsea s\u1ebd l\u00e0 \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7 \u0111\u00e1ng g\u1eddm trong cu\u1ed9c \u0111ua v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch. C\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u0110\u1ee9c cho r\u1eb1ng, The Blues \u0111\u00e3 \u0111em v\u1ec1 m\u1ed9t chi\u1ebfn l\u01b0\u1ee3c gia xu\u1ea5t s\u1eafc c\u00f9ng l\u1ed1i ch\u01a1i t\u1ea5n c\u00f4ng \u0111\u1eb9p m\u1eaft. &ldquo;\u0110\u00f3 s\u1ebd l\u00e0 \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7 l\u1edbn nh\u1ea5t c\u1ee7a ch\u00fang t\u00f4i, h\u00e3y nh\u00ecn c\u00e1ch Napoli thi \u0111\u1ea5u m\u00e0 xem&rdquo; &ndash; Sane cho bi\u1ebft.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"\u0110i\u1ec3m tin b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 s\u00e1ng 24/7 Ai l\u00e0 \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7 l\u1edbn nh\u1ea5t c\u1ee7a Man City h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"\u0110i\u1ec3m tin b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 s\u00e1ng 247 Ai l\u00e0 \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7 l\u1edbn nh\u1ea5t c\u1ee7a Man City h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/6/28/Diem-tin-bong-da-sang-247-Ai-la-doi-thu-lon-nhat-cua-Man-City-hinh-anh.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>\u0110i\u1ec3m tin b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 24/7: Sane \u0111\u00e1nh gi\u00e1 cao Chelsea</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<h3>&nbsp;</h3>\r\n</div>\r\n<h2>Chelsea ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c \u0111\u00f2i h\u1ecfi kh\u00f3 Barca<br>\r\n&nbsp;</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Sau khi CLB T\u00e2y Ban Nha \u0111\u01b0a ra l\u1eddi \u0111\u1ec1 ngh\u1ecb th\u1ee9 3 tr\u1ecb gi\u00e1 55 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng cho Willian b\u1ecb t\u1eeb ch\u1ed1i, \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng n\u00e0y ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c g\u1eb7ng h\u1ecfi m\u1ee9c gi\u00e1 65 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng. Tuy nhi\u00ean, b\u00e1o ch\u00ed Anh cho bi\u1ebft Chelsea s\u1ebd kh\u00f4ng ch\u1ea5p nh\u1eadn b\u1ea5t k\u1ef3 l\u1eddi \u0111\u1ec1 ngh\u1ecb n\u00e0o d\u01b0\u1edbi&hellip; 70 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng. Ho\u1eb7c ch\u1ecbu chi ra s\u1ed1 ti\u1ec1n kh\u1ed5ng l\u1ed3, ho\u1eb7c Barcelona s\u1ebd th\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i v\u1edbi m\u1ee5c ti\u00eau n\u00e0y.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<h2>M.U \u0111\u1eb7t gi\u00e1 kh\u1ee7ng cho Martial<br>\r\n&nbsp;</h2>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\">C\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi Ph\u00e1p \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c cho l\u00e0 mu\u1ed1n r\u1eddi Man United \u0111\u1ec3 t\u00ecm ki\u1ebfm su\u1ea5t \u0111\u00e1 ch\u00ednh, v\u00e0 c\u0169ng t\u1eeb ch\u1ed1i gia h\u1ea1n h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng, m\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y \u0111\u00e3 b\u1ecb Mourinho treo gi\u00e1. Theo \u0111\u00f3, Ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u0111\u1eb7c bi\u1ec7t mu\u1ed1n thu v\u1ec1 50 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng cho c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 sinh n\u0103m 1995, c\u00f9ng \u0111i\u1ec1u ki\u1ec7n ch\u1ec9 b\u00e1n anh b\u00ean ngo\u00e0i Premier League. Bayern v\u00e0 Juve l\u00e0 2 \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng mu\u1ed1n c\u00f3 ch\u1eef k\u00fd t\u00e0i n\u0103ng ng\u01b0\u1eddi Ph\u00e1p.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<h2>Chelsea chu\u1ea9n b\u1ecb mua s\u1eafm ho\u1ea3ng lo\u1ea1n</h2>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Theo \u0111\u00f3, \u0111\u1ed9i ch\u1ee7 s\u00e2n Stamford Bridge chu\u1ea9n b\u1ecb \u0111em v\u1ec1 Pepe Reina, th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n k\u1ef3 c\u1ef1u n\u0103m nay 35 tu\u1ed5i v\u1edbi m\u1ee9c gi\u00e1 9 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng. \u0110\u00e1ng ch\u00fa \u00fd, Reina l\u00e0 tr\u00f2 c\u0169 c\u1ee7a HLV Sarri t\u1ea1i Napoli, nh\u01b0ng anh m\u1edbi chuy\u1ec3n sang AC Milan ngay m\u00f9a h\u00e8 n\u00e0y d\u01b0\u1edbi d\u1ea1ng chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng t\u1ef1 do. N\u1ebfu th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng, \u0111\u00e2y s\u1ebd l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t th\u01b0\u01a1ng v\u1ee5 r\u1ea5t h\u00e0i h\u01b0\u1edbc c\u1ee7a The Blues, c\u00f2n nh\u1eefng ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u1edf Milan b\u1ed7ng d\u01b0ng c\u00f3 9 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"\u0110i\u1ec3m tin b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 s\u00e1ng 24/7\" title=\"thu mon Pepe Reina toi Milan\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/3/12/thu-mon-pepe-reina-toi-milan-kiem-tra-y-te.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>\u0110i\u1ec3m tin b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 24/7: Pepe Reina m\u1edbi t\u1edbi Milan v\u00e0 \u0111ang \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c Chelsea h\u1ecfi mua</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<h3>&nbsp;</h3>\r\n</div>\r\n<h2>Karius tr\u00e1ch c\u1ee9 Liverpool v\u00ec mua ng\u01b0\u1eddi<br>\r\n&nbsp;</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">The Kop m\u1edbi k\u00edch n\u1ed5 bom t\u1ea5n Alisson tr\u1ecb gi\u00e1 67 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng, t\u1ea5t nhi\u00ean ng\u01b0\u1eddi kh\u00f4ng h\u00e0i l\u00f2ng nh\u1ea5t l\u00e0 Loris Karius. M\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y, anh \u0111\u00e3 t\u1ecf ra kh\u00f3 ch\u1ecbu khi CLB kh\u00f4ng b\u00e1o tr\u01b0\u1edbc v\u1edbi m\u00ecnh v\u00e0 \u0111em v\u1ec1 m\u1ed9t th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n m\u1edbi. \u0110\u1ed3ng th\u1eddi, Karius c\u0169ng th\u1eeba nh\u1eadn anh kh\u00f4ng bi\u1ebft nh\u1eefng g\u00ec m\u00ecnh \u0111ang l\u00e0m l\u00e0 \u0111\u00fang hay sai, sau v\u00f4 v\u00e0n nh\u1eefng ch\u1ec9 tr\u00edch t\u1eeb sau tr\u1eadn chung k\u1ebft Champions League.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">T\u1ed5ng h\u1ee3p &ndash; TTVN</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"1554","checkdouble":"191869"},{"date":"01:26 24/07","title":"Mbappe x\u00fai gi\u1ee5c Kante b\u1ecf Chelsea sang PSG","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/23/mbappe-xui-giuc-kante-bo-chelsea-sang-psg.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Th\u1ea7n \u0111\u1ed3ng Kylian Mbappe ti\u1ebft l\u1ed9 \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c ch\u1ee7 t\u1ecbch PSG nh\u1edd c\u1eady l\u00f4i k\u00e9o \u0111\u1ed3ng h\u01b0\u01a1ng N\u2019Golo Kante tr\u1edf v\u1ec1 Ph\u00e1p trong su\u1ed1t chi\u1ebfn d\u1ecbch World Cup 2018.</h2><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">\u0110\u00f3ng g\u00f3p vai tr\u00f2 t\u1ed1i quan tr\u1ecdng gi\u00fap \u0111\u1ed9i tuy\u1ec3n Ph\u00e1p \u0111\u0103ng quang ng\u00f4i v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch th\u1ebf gi\u1edbi v\u1edbi c\u00fap v\u00e0ng th\u1ee9 hai trong l\u1ecbch s\u1eed, t\u00e0i n\u0103ng v\u00e0 \u0111\u1eb3ng c\u1ea5p c\u1ee7a N\u2019Golo Kante m\u1ed9t l\u1ea7n n\u1eefa khi\u1ebfn c\u00e1c \u00f4ng l\u1edbn Ch\u00e2u \u00c2u ph\u1ea3i th\u00e8m kh\u00e1t v\u00e0 quy\u1ebft t\u00e2m s\u1edf h\u1eefu b\u1eb1ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c ch\u1eef k\u00fd c\u1ee7a anh.</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\"><o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">C\u00f3 l\u1ebd nghi\u00eam t\u00fac h\u01a1n c\u1ea3 ch\u00ednh l\u00e0 \u0111\u1ea1i gia Paris Saint-Germain, th\u1eadm ch\u00ed nh\u01b0 theo ti\u1ebft l\u1ed9 c\u1ee7a Kylian Mbappe, m\u1ed9t ng\u00f4i sao kh\u00e1c c\u0169ng \u0111\u00e3 ch\u00f3i s\u00e1ng r\u1ef1c r\u1ee1 tr\u00ean \u0111\u1ea5t Nga, gi\u1edbi ch\u1ee7 \u1ea2 R\u1eadp \u0111\u00e3 nh\u1edd c\u1eady anh ch\u1ee7 \u0111\u1ed9ng l\u00f4i k\u00e9o \u0111\u1ed3ng h\u01b0\u01a1ng c\u1eadp b\u1ebfn \u201cC\u00f4ng vi\u00ean c\u00e1c Ho\u00e0ng t\u1eed\u201d trong su\u1ed1t chi\u1ebfn d\u1ecbch World Cup 2018.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Mbappe x\u00fai gi\u1ee5c Kante b\u1ecf Chelsea sang PSG h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Mbappe x\u00fai gi\u1ee5c Kante b\u1ecf Chelsea sang PSG h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/23/mbappe-xui-giuc-kante-bo-chelsea-sang-psg.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Mbappe x\u00fai gi\u1ee5c Kante b\u1ecf Chelsea sang PSG</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">Th\u1ea7n \u0111\u1ed3ng tu\u1ed5i teen ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u: \u201c\u0110\u00fang l\u00e0 ng\u00e0i ch\u1ee7 t\u1ecbch \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 l\u1eddi v\u1edbi t\u00f4i v\u00e0 t\u00f4i c\u0169ng \u0111\u00e3 chuy\u1ec3n n\u00f3 \u0111\u1ebfn cho N\u2019Golo khi anh em g\u1eb7p nhau \u1edf World Cup trong m\u00e0u \u00e1o \u0111\u1ed9i tuy\u1ec3n qu\u1ed1c gia.\u201d<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">\u201cTuy nhi\u00ean, t\u00f4i c\u0169ng kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 n\u00f3i qu\u00e1 nhi\u1ec1u v\u1edbi anh \u1ea5y v\u1ec1 chuy\u1ec7n n\u00e0y, hi\u1ec3u r\u1eb1ng v\u1ea5n \u0111\u1ec1 t\u01b0\u01a1ng lai hay chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 \u1ea3nh h\u01b0\u1edfng nghi\u00eam tr\u1ecdng ra sao \u0111\u1ebfn phong \u0111\u1ed9 v\u00e0 t\u00e2m l\u00fd thi \u0111\u1ea5u.\u201d<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">\u201cTh\u1ebf l\u00e0 t\u00f4i g\u1eedi qua m\u1ea9u m\u1ea5u gi\u1ea5y \u0111\u00fat t\u00fai N\u2019Golo, hy v\u1ecdng r\u1eb1ng anh \u1ea5y s\u1ebd ph\u00e1t hi\u1ec7n v\u00e0 \u0111em ra \u0111\u1ecdc \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c tin nh\u1eafn t\u1eeb PSG. Anh \u1ea5y th\u1ef1c s\u1ef1 l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 xu\u1ea5t s\u1eafc m\u00e0 \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng n\u00e0o c\u0169ng mu\u1ed1n c\u00f3, v\u00e0 ch\u00fang t\u00f4i ch\u1eafc ch\u1eafn kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 l\u00e0 ngo\u1ea1i l\u1ec7.\u201d<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">N\u00f3i v\u1eady th\u00f4i ch\u1ee9 \u0111\u1ec3 cu\u1ed7m Kante ra kh\u1ecfi Chelsea th\u00ec g\u1ea7n nh\u01b0 l\u00e0 nhi\u1ec7m v\u1ee5 b\u1ea5t kh\u1ea3 thi \u1edf th\u1eddi \u0111i\u1ec3m hi\u1ec7n t\u1ea1i. Ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 ph\u00f2ng ng\u1ef1 ng\u01b0\u1eddi Ph\u00e1p \u0111\u01a1n gi\u1ea3n kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 thay th\u1ebf \u1edf Stamford Bridge, \u0111\u1eb7c bi\u1ec7t d\u01b0\u1edbi tri\u1ec1u \u0111\u1ea1i m\u1edbi c\u1ee7a t\u00e2n HLV Maurizio Sarri.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/qua-de-thuong-kante-ngo-tau-ngai-di-hoi-xin-nho-ban-muon-ho-cup-vang-de-song-ao-421-191369.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/16/qua-de-thuong-kante-ngo-tau-ngai-di-hoi-xin-nho-ban-muon-ho-cup-vang-de-song-ao.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/qua-de-thuong-kante-ngo-tau-ngai-di-hoi-xin-nho-ban-muon-ho-cup-vang-de-song-ao-421-191369.html\">Qu\u00e1 d\u1ec5 th\u01b0\u01a1ng! Kante ng\u1ed1 t\u00e0u ng\u1ea1i \u0111i h\u1ecfi xin, nh\u1edd b\u1ea1n m\u01b0\u1ee3n h\u1ed9 c\u00fap v\u00e0ng \u0111\u1ec3 s\u1ed1ng \u1ea3o</span><br>\r\nTi\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 ph\u00f2ng ng\u1ef1 c\u1ee7a Chelsea ch\u00ednh l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t trong nh\u1eefng c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 quan tr\u1ecdng nh\u1ea5t c\u1ee7a \u0111\u1ed9i tuy\u1ec3n Ph\u00e1p tr\u00ean h\u00e0nh tr\u00ecnh v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch World Cup 2018.</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\"><strong>Gia Khoa (TTVN)</strong> <o:p></o:p></p></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"1553","checkdouble":"191870"},{"date":"00:00 24/07","title":"L\u0110B\u0110 \u0110\u1ee9c ph\u1ea3n ph\u00e1o Ozil sau c\u00e1o bu\u1ed9c ph\u00e2n bi\u1ec7t ch\u1ee7ng t\u1ed9c","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/23/ldbd-duc-phan-phao-ozil-sau-cao-buoc-phan-biet-chung-toc.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>L\u0110B\u0110 \u0110\u1ee9c ch\u00ednh th\u1ee9c \u0111\u01b0a ra th\u00f4ng b\u00e1o ph\u1ea3n ph\u00e1o nh\u1eefng l\u1eddi ch\u1ec9 tr\u00edch, c\u00e1o bu\u1ed9c ph\u00e2n bi\u1ec7t ch\u1ee7ng t\u1ed9c \u0111\u1ebfn t\u1eeb Mesut Ozil, sau khi ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 29 tu\u1ed5i quy\u1ebft \u0111\u1ecbnh gi\u00e3 t\u1eeb s\u1ef1 nghi\u1ec7p qu\u1ed1c t\u1ebf trong n\u1ed7i u\u1ea5t h\u1eadn.</h2><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">B\u1ea5t ng\u1edd v\u00e0 g\u00e2y x\u00f4n xao, b\u00e0ng ho\u00e0ng d\u01b0 lu\u1eadn, Mesut Ozil quy\u1ebft \u0111\u1ecbnh chia tay \u0111\u1ed9i tuy\u1ec3n \u0110\u1ee9c khi ch\u1ec9 m\u1edbi \u1edf tu\u1ed5i 29, b\u1ecf l\u1ea1i 9 n\u0103m g\u1eafn b\u00f3 x\u1ee9ng danh c\u00f4ng th\u1ea7n v\u1edbi 23 b\u00e0n/92 tr\u1eadn c\u00f9ng ng\u00f4i v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch World Cup 2014.</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\"><o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">Ng\u00f4i sao Arsenal b\u1ecb ch\u1ec9 tr\u00edch n\u1eb7ng n\u1ec1 h\u01a1n b\u1ea5t c\u1ee9 ai sau chi\u1ebfn d\u1ecbch World Cup 2018 th\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i th\u1ea3m h\u1ecda c\u1ee7a Mannschaft. Nguy\u00ean nh\u00e2n th\u1eadm ch\u00ed c\u00f2n s\u00e2u xa h\u01a1n v\u1eady khi n\u00f3 d\u01b0\u1eddng nh\u01b0 b\u1eaft ngu\u1ed3n ch\u00ednh g\u1ed1c g\u00e1c nh\u1eadp c\u01b0 t\u1eeb Th\u1ed5 Nh\u0129 K\u1ef3 v\u00e0 khi\u1ebfn anh b\u1ecb c\u00f4 l\u1eadp, gh\u00e9t b\u1ecf hay g\u1ea7n nh\u01b0 k\u1ef3 th\u1ecb, ph\u00e2n bi\u1ec7t ch\u1ee7ng t\u1ed9c.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"L\u0110B\u0110 ph\u1ea3n ph\u00e1o c\u00e1o bu\u1ed9c c\u1ee7a Ozil chia tay \u0111\u1ed9i tuy\u1ec3n \u0110\u1ee9c h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"L\u0110B\u0110 ph\u1ea3n ph\u00e1o c\u00e1o bu\u1ed9c c\u1ee7a Ozil chia tay \u0111\u1ed9i tuy\u1ec3n \u0110\u1ee9c h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/23/ldbd-duc-phan-phao-ozil-sau-cao-buoc-phan-biet-chung-toc.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 Mesut Ozil chia tay \u0111\u1ed9i tuy\u1ec3n \u0110\u1ee9c v\u00e0 b\u1ecb L\u0110B\u0110 n\u01b0\u1edbc nh\u00e0 ph\u1ea3n ph\u00e1o v\u00ec c\u00e1o bu\u1ed9c ph\u00e2n bi\u1ec7t ch\u1ee7ng t\u1ed9c</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">Tuy nhi\u00ean m\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y, \u0111\u00edch th\u00e2n L\u0110B\u0110 \u0110\u1ee9c \u0111\u00e3 l\u00ean ti\u1ebfng ph\u1ea3n ph\u00e1o v\u1edbi m\u1ed9t b\u1ea3n th\u00f4ng b\u00e1o d\u00e0i \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111\u0103ng tr\u00ean trang ch\u1ee7 c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh. N\u1ed9i dung c\u01a1 b\u1ea3n \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c vi\u1ebft nh\u01b0 sau:<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">\u201cNh\u1eefng b\u1ee9c h\u00ecnh ch\u1ee5p chung v\u1edbi t\u1ed5ng th\u1ed1ng Th\u1ed5 Nh\u0129 K\u1ef3 Recep Tayyip Erdogan d\u1ea5y l\u00ean nh\u1eefng d\u1ea5u h\u1ecfi lo ng\u1ea1i trong l\u00f2ng x\u00e3 h\u1ed9i \u0110\u1ee9c. Ch\u00fang t\u00f4i c\u0169ng th\u1eeba nh\u1eadn L\u0110B\u0110 \u0110\u1ee9c c\u00f3 m\u1ed9t ph\u1ea7n tr\u00e1ch nhi\u1ec7m trong s\u1ef1 v\u1ee5 l\u1ea7n n\u00e0y. B\u00ean c\u1ea1nh \u0111\u00f3, ch\u00fang t\u00f4i c\u0169ng r\u1ea5t l\u1ea5y l\u00e0m ti\u1ebfc khi Mesut Ozil c\u00f3 c\u1ea3m nh\u1eadn r\u1eb1ng anh \u1ea5y kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c b\u1ea3o v\u1ec7 tr\u01b0\u1edbc v\u1ea5n n\u1ea1n ph\u00e2n bi\u1ec7t ch\u1ee7ng t\u1ed9c, trong khi Jerome Boateng th\u00ec ho\u00e0n to\u00e0n r\u1ea5t \u1ed5n.\u201d<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">\u201cL\u0110B\u0110 \u0110\u1ee9c s\u1ebd v\u00f4 c\u00f9ng h\u1ea1nh ph\u00fac n\u1ebfu Mesut Ozil v\u1eabn l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t th\u00e0nh vi\u00ean trong \u0111\u1ed9i tuy\u1ec3n qu\u1ed1c gia, nh\u01b0ng r\u1ed3i anh \u1ea5y \u0111\u00e3 quy\u1ebft \u0111\u1ecbnh l\u1ef1a ch\u1ecdn h\u01b0\u1edbng \u0111i ri\u00eang cho m\u00ecnh. Ch\u00fang t\u00f4i ho\u00e0n to\u00e0n t\u00f4n tr\u1ecdng anh \u1ea5y v\u00e0 \u0111\u1ec3 th\u1ec3 hi\u1ec7n \u0111i\u1ec1u \u0111\u00f3, ch\u00fang t\u00f4i \u0111\u00e3 v\u00e0 s\u1ebd kh\u00f4ng tr\u1ea3 l\u1eddi nh\u1eefng c\u00e1o bu\u1ed9c v\u00f4 l\u00fd v\u1ec1 m\u00ecnh m\u1ed9t c\u00e1ch c\u00f4ng khai.\u201d<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">\u201cCh\u00fang t\u00f4i xin nh\u1ea5n m\u1ea1nh L\u0110B\u0110 \u0110\u1ee9c kh\u00f4ng bao gi\u1edd c\u00f3 t\u01b0 t\u01b0\u1edfng ph\u00e2n bi\u1ec7t ch\u1ee7ng t\u1ed9c v\u1edbi b\u1ea5t c\u1ee9 ai tr\u00ean th\u1ebf gi\u1edbi. Th\u1ef1c t\u1ebf, ch\u00fang t\u00f4i \u0111\u00e3 t\u00edc c\u1ef1c tham gia h\u1ed7 tr\u1ee3 c\u00f4ng t\u00e1c nh\u1eadp c\u01b0 cho \u0111\u1ea5t n\u01b0\u1edbc trong r\u1ea5t nhi\u1ec1u n\u0103m qua.\u201d<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/nhan-vat/mesut-\u00f6zil-nan-nhan-dien-hinh-cua-mot-nuoc-duc-chia-re-vi-chinh-sach-nhap-cu-389-191848.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/23/mesut-zil-nan-nhan-dien-hinh-cua-mot-nuoc-duc-chia-re-vi-chinh-sach-nhap-cu.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/nhan-vat/mesut-\u00f6zil-nan-nhan-dien-hinh-cua-mot-nuoc-duc-chia-re-vi-chinh-sach-nhap-cu-389-191848.html\">Mesut \u00d6zil: N\u1ea1n nh\u00e2n \u0111i\u1ec3n h\u00ecnh c\u1ee7a m\u1ed9t n\u01b0\u1edbc \u0110\u1ee9c chia r\u1ebd v\u00ec ch\u00ednh s\u00e1ch nh\u1eadp c\u01b0</span><br>\r\nSau \u00d6zil h\u00f4m nay, t\u01b0\u01a1ng lai s\u1ebd c\u00f2n bao nhi\u00eau \u00d6zil n\u1eefa? V\u00e0 nh\u1eefng t\u00e0i n\u0103ng c\u00f3 g\u1ed1c g\u00e1c n\u01b0\u1edbc ngo\u00e0i kh\u00e1c, \u0111ang tr\u01b0\u1edfng th\u00e0nh trong nh\u1eefng H\u1ecdc vi\u1ec7n b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 \u0110\u1ee9c, khi...</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\"><strong>Gia Khoa (TTVN)</strong><o:p></o:p></p></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"1552","checkdouble":"191871"},{"date":"06:16 24/07","title":"\u0110i\u1ec3m tin b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 s\u00e1ng 24/7: B\u1ea5t ng\u1edd v\u1edbi \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7 l\u1edbn nh\u1ea5t c\u1ee7a Man City m\u00f9a sau","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/6/5/diem-tin-bong-da-sang-247-bat-ngo-voi-doi-thu-lon-nhat-cua-man-city-mua-sau.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>D\u01b0\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y l\u00e0 nh\u1eefng tin t\u1ee9c t\u1ed5ng h\u1ee3p \u0111\u00e1ng ch\u00fa \u00fd trong ph\u1ea7n \u0111i\u1ec3m tin b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 tr\u00ean chuy\u00ean trang Bongda24h s\u00e1ng ng\u00e0y 24/7. \r\n</h2><h2><br>\r\n\u0110\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng n\u00e0o s\u1ebd c\u1ea3n b\u01b0\u1edbc Man City \u1edf m\u00f9a sau?<br>\r\n&nbsp;</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">M\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y, ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 Leroy Sane \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u01b0a ra nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh kh\u00e1 b\u1ea5t ng\u1edd, khi cho r\u1eb1ng Chelsea s\u1ebd l\u00e0 \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7 \u0111\u00e1ng g\u1eddm trong cu\u1ed9c \u0111ua v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch. C\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u0110\u1ee9c cho r\u1eb1ng, The Blues \u0111\u00e3 \u0111em v\u1ec1 m\u1ed9t chi\u1ebfn l\u01b0\u1ee3c gia xu\u1ea5t s\u1eafc c\u00f9ng l\u1ed1i ch\u01a1i t\u1ea5n c\u00f4ng \u0111\u1eb9p m\u1eaft. &ldquo;\u0110\u00f3 s\u1ebd l\u00e0 \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7 l\u1edbn nh\u1ea5t c\u1ee7a ch\u00fang t\u00f4i, h\u00e3y nh\u00ecn c\u00e1ch Napoli thi \u0111\u1ea5u m\u00e0 xem&rdquo; &ndash; Sane cho bi\u1ebft.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"\u0110i\u1ec3m tin b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 s\u00e1ng 24/7 Ai l\u00e0 \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7 l\u1edbn nh\u1ea5t c\u1ee7a Man City h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"\u0110i\u1ec3m tin b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 s\u00e1ng 247 Ai l\u00e0 \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7 l\u1edbn nh\u1ea5t c\u1ee7a Man City h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/6/28/Diem-tin-bong-da-sang-247-Ai-la-doi-thu-lon-nhat-cua-Man-City-hinh-anh.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>\u0110i\u1ec3m tin b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 24/7: Sane \u0111\u00e1nh gi\u00e1 cao Chelsea</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<h3>&nbsp;</h3>\r\n</div>\r\n<h2>Chelsea ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c \u0111\u00f2i h\u1ecfi kh\u00f3 Barca<br>\r\n&nbsp;</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Sau khi CLB T\u00e2y Ban Nha \u0111\u01b0a ra l\u1eddi \u0111\u1ec1 ngh\u1ecb th\u1ee9 3 tr\u1ecb gi\u00e1 55 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng cho Willian b\u1ecb t\u1eeb ch\u1ed1i, \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng n\u00e0y ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c g\u1eb7ng h\u1ecfi m\u1ee9c gi\u00e1 65 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng. Tuy nhi\u00ean, b\u00e1o ch\u00ed Anh cho bi\u1ebft Chelsea s\u1ebd kh\u00f4ng ch\u1ea5p nh\u1eadn b\u1ea5t k\u1ef3 l\u1eddi \u0111\u1ec1 ngh\u1ecb n\u00e0o d\u01b0\u1edbi&hellip; 70 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng. Ho\u1eb7c ch\u1ecbu chi ra s\u1ed1 ti\u1ec1n kh\u1ed5ng l\u1ed3, ho\u1eb7c Barcelona s\u1ebd th\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i v\u1edbi m\u1ee5c ti\u00eau n\u00e0y.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<h2>M.U \u0111\u1eb7t gi\u00e1 kh\u1ee7ng cho Martial<br>\r\n&nbsp;</h2>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\">C\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi Ph\u00e1p \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c cho l\u00e0 mu\u1ed1n r\u1eddi Man United \u0111\u1ec3 t\u00ecm ki\u1ebfm su\u1ea5t \u0111\u00e1 ch\u00ednh, v\u00e0 c\u0169ng t\u1eeb ch\u1ed1i gia h\u1ea1n h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng, m\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y \u0111\u00e3 b\u1ecb Mourinho treo gi\u00e1. Theo \u0111\u00f3, Ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u0111\u1eb7c bi\u1ec7t mu\u1ed1n thu v\u1ec1 50 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng cho c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 sinh n\u0103m 1995, c\u00f9ng \u0111i\u1ec1u ki\u1ec7n ch\u1ec9 b\u00e1n anh b\u00ean ngo\u00e0i Premier League. Bayern v\u00e0 Juve l\u00e0 2 \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng mu\u1ed1n c\u00f3 ch\u1eef k\u00fd t\u00e0i n\u0103ng ng\u01b0\u1eddi Ph\u00e1p.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<h2>Chelsea chu\u1ea9n b\u1ecb mua s\u1eafm ho\u1ea3ng lo\u1ea1n</h2>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Theo \u0111\u00f3, \u0111\u1ed9i ch\u1ee7 s\u00e2n Stamford Bridge chu\u1ea9n b\u1ecb \u0111em v\u1ec1 Pepe Reina, th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n k\u1ef3 c\u1ef1u n\u0103m nay 35 tu\u1ed5i v\u1edbi m\u1ee9c gi\u00e1 9 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng. \u0110\u00e1ng ch\u00fa \u00fd, Reina l\u00e0 tr\u00f2 c\u0169 c\u1ee7a HLV Sarri t\u1ea1i Napoli, nh\u01b0ng anh m\u1edbi chuy\u1ec3n sang AC Milan ngay m\u00f9a h\u00e8 n\u00e0y d\u01b0\u1edbi d\u1ea1ng chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng t\u1ef1 do. N\u1ebfu th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng, \u0111\u00e2y s\u1ebd l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t th\u01b0\u01a1ng v\u1ee5 r\u1ea5t h\u00e0i h\u01b0\u1edbc c\u1ee7a The Blues, c\u00f2n nh\u1eefng ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u1edf Milan b\u1ed7ng d\u01b0ng c\u00f3 9 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"\u0110i\u1ec3m tin b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 s\u00e1ng 24/7\" title=\"thu mon Pepe Reina toi Milan\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/3/12/thu-mon-pepe-reina-toi-milan-kiem-tra-y-te.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>\u0110i\u1ec3m tin b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 24/7: Pepe Reina m\u1edbi t\u1edbi Milan v\u00e0 \u0111ang \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c Chelsea h\u1ecfi mua</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<h3>&nbsp;</h3>\r\n</div>\r\n<h2>Karius tr\u00e1ch c\u1ee9 Liverpool v\u00ec mua ng\u01b0\u1eddi<br>\r\n&nbsp;</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">The Kop m\u1edbi k\u00edch n\u1ed5 bom t\u1ea5n Alisson tr\u1ecb gi\u00e1 67 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng, t\u1ea5t nhi\u00ean ng\u01b0\u1eddi kh\u00f4ng h\u00e0i l\u00f2ng nh\u1ea5t l\u00e0 Loris Karius. M\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y, anh \u0111\u00e3 t\u1ecf ra kh\u00f3 ch\u1ecbu khi CLB kh\u00f4ng b\u00e1o tr\u01b0\u1edbc v\u1edbi m\u00ecnh v\u00e0 \u0111em v\u1ec1 m\u1ed9t th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n m\u1edbi. \u0110\u1ed3ng th\u1eddi, Karius c\u0169ng th\u1eeba nh\u1eadn anh kh\u00f4ng bi\u1ebft nh\u1eefng g\u00ec m\u00ecnh \u0111ang l\u00e0m l\u00e0 \u0111\u00fang hay sai, sau v\u00f4 v\u00e0n nh\u1eefng ch\u1ec9 tr\u00edch t\u1eeb sau tr\u1eadn chung k\u1ebft Champions League.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">T\u1ed5ng h\u1ee3p &ndash; TTVN</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"1551","checkdouble":"191872"}]}